hadiths[258]{hadithnumber,text}:
5127,"Hajjaj-bin Muhammad ne ibne-Juraij se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey ibne-Shahab ne Ali-bin Husain bin Ali se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid Husain bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath badr ke maale-ghanimat mein se aik (jawan) ontni hasil hui. aik aur jawan ontni (khums mein se) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey ata farmai. aik din maine un donon oontniyon ko aik Ansari ke darwazey par bithaya aur main un donon par bechney ke liye izkhir (ki khushbu daar ghaas) laadkar lana chahta tha. padhi. banu-Qainuqaa ka sunaar bhi mere sath tha. padhi. aur us (ki qeemat) se main Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) (ke sath apni shadi) ke waleemey mein madad lena chahta tha. Hamza bin abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) us ghar main (baithey) sharab pi rahe they, unke qareeb aik gaane wali aurat ga rahi thi phir wo ye ashaar gaane lagi sunein Hamza! (uth kar) farba oontniyon ki taraf badhein (doosra misra hai. ( وَهُنَّ مُعَلَّقَاتٌ بِالْفِنَاءِ (aur ghar ke aagey khuli jagah mein bandhi hui hain.) Hazrat Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) talwaar samet lapak kar unki taraf badhey unke kohaanon ko jad se kaat liya unke pehlu cheer diye phir unke kalejey nikal liye. maine ibne-Shahab se kaha : aur kohan bhi? unhon-ne kaha : wo (Hamza (Raziallahu anhu)) un donon ke kohan jad se kaat kar ley gaey. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine aik aisa manzar dekha jisne mujhey dehla kar rakh diya. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua Zaid-bin-Haarisa (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap ke paas maujood they. aap Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath nikal padey. main bhi aap ke sath chalney laga. aap hazraat Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur ghussey ka izhar farmaya, Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ne aankh uthai aur kehney lagey : tum mere aabaa-w ajdaad ke ghulaamon se badh kar kya ho! (wo donon janab abdul-Muttalib ke potey they aur rishtey ke hawale se khidmat guzari ke maqam par they. Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) rishtey mein unse aik pusht uper they. unhon-ne sharab ki lahar mein usi baat ko mubaalgha aamez fakhr w mubaahaat ke rang mein keh diya) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ultey paon wapas huey aur unki mahfil se nikal aaey."
5128,Abdur-Razzaq ne ibne-Juraij se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5129,"Abdullah-bin Wahab ne kaha : mujhey Yunus bin Yazeed ne ibne-Shahab se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Ali-bin Husain bin Ali ne bataya ke Husain bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khabar di ke Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke mujhey badr ke din maale-ghanimat mein aik ontni mili aur isi din aik ontni Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey khums mein se aur di. phir jab maine chaha ke Fatima zohra (Raziallahu anhu) se shadi karun jo ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sahibzadi thin to maine bani qainuqaa ke aik sunaar se wada kya ke wo mere sath chaley aur ham donon mil kar izkhir laaein aur sunaaron ke hath bechein aur us se main apni shadi ka walima karun. main apni donon oontniyon ka saman paalaan, rakaabein aur rassiyaan wghaira ikattha kar raha tha aur wo donon oontniyan aik Ansari ki kothri ke bazu mein baithi thin. jis waqt main ye saman jo ikattha kar raha tha ikattha karke lota to kya dekhta hun ke donon oontniyon ke kohan katey huey hain, unki kokhein phati hui hain aur unke jigar nikal liye gaey mujh se ye dekh kar na raha gaya aur meri aankhen tham na sakein (yani mein roney laga ye rona duniya ke tama se na tha balke Sayeda Fatima zohra (Raziallahu anhu) aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke haq mein jo taqseer hui, us khayal se tha) maine puchha ke ye kis ne kiya? logon ne kaha ke Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) bin abdul-Muttalib ne aur wo us ghar mein Ansar ki aik jamat ke sath hain jo sharab pi rahe hain, unke samney aur unke sathiyon ke samney aik gaaney wali ne gaana gaaya to gaaney mein ye kaha ke aey Hamza uth un moti oontniyon ko usi waqt ley. Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) talwaar lekar uthey aur unke kohan kaat liye aur kokhein phaad daalein aur jigar (kaleja) nikal liya. saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye sun kar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas gaya, wahan Zaid-bin-Haarisa (Raziallahu anhu) baithey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey dekhtey hi mere chehrey se ranj w museebat ko pehchan liya aur farmaya ke tujh ko kya hua? maine arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! Allah ki qism ! aaj ka sa din maine kabhi nahi dekha. Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ne meri donon oontniyon par zulm kya, unke kohan kaat liye, kokhein phaad daalein aur wo us ghar mein chand sharaabiyon ke sath hain. ye sun kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni chadar mangwa kar odhi aur phir paidal chaley, main aur Zaid-bin-Haarisa donon Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey they, yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us darwazey par aaey jahan Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) they aur andar aaney ki ijazat mangi. logon ne ijazat di. dekha to wo sharab piey huey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saiyedna Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ko us kaam par malaamat shuru ki aur saiyedna Hamza ki aankhen (nashey ki wjah se) surkh thin unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghutnon ko dekha, phir nigaah buland ki to naaf ko dekha. phir nigaah buland ki to munh ko dekha aur (nashey mein dhut honey ki wjah se) kaha ke tum to mere bap daadon ke ghulam ho. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pehchaana ke wo nashe mein mast hain to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ultey paon phirey aur bahar nikley. ham bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley."
5130,Abdullah-bin-Mubarak ne Yunus se unhon-ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5131,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jis din sharab haram ki gaee, mein Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar ( logon ko) sharab pilaa raha tha. unki sharab adh-pakki aur khushk khajooron se taiyaar shuda sharab ke siwa aur koi na thi, itney mein aik elaan karne wala pukarney laga. unhon-ne kaha : main jaun aur dekhun to ( dekha ke wahan ( aik manaadi elaan kar raha tha : ( logo ( suno ! sharab haram kar di gaee. kaha : phir Madina ki galiyon mein sharab bahney lagi abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se kaha : niklo aur usey baha do! maine wo (sab ( baha di. to logon ne kaha, padhi. ya unmein se kuchh ne kaha, padhi. falan Shahid hua tha aur falan Shahid hua tha to ye (sharab) unke pet mein maujood thi. padhi. (eik rawi ne) kaha : mujhey malum nahi ye (bhi) Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis mein se hai (ya nahi). is par Allah Taala ne لَيْسَ عَلَى ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا وَعَمِلُوا ٱلصَّلِحَٰتِ جُنَاحٌ فِيمَا طَعِمُوٓا إِذَا مَا ٱتَّقَوا وَّءَامَنُوا وَعَمِلُوا ٱلصَّلِحَٰتِ nazil farmai : jo log eman laey aur nek kaam kiye jab unhon-ne taqwa ikhtiyar kya eman laey aur nek amal kiye (to ( un par us cheez ke sabab koi gunah nahi jis ko unhon-ne ( hurmat se pahley) khaya piyaa ( tha. ("
5132,"Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb ne kaha : logon ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se fazeekh (mili juli kachchi aur pakki hui khajooron ka ras jis mein Khumair uth jaey) ke mutaalliq sawal kya. unhon-ne kaha : tumharey us fazeekh ke ilawa hamari koi sharab thi hi nahi yahi sharab thi jis ko tum fazeekh kehtey ho, main apne ghar mein khadey ho kar yahi sharab Hazrat abu Talha Hazrat abu Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke doosrey sathiyon ko pilaa raha tha ke aik shakhs aaya aur kehney laga : tumhen khabar pahunchi? ham ne kaha : nahi. usne kaha : sharab haram kar di gaee hai. to (abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Anas! (sharab ke) ye sarey matkey baha do. us aadmi ke khabar dene ke baad un logon ne na kabhi sharab pi aur na iske barey mein (kabhi) kuchh poochha."
5133,"ibne-Ulaih ne kaha : hamein Sulaiman Taimi ne bataya kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : main apne qabeeley walon apne chachaon ko unki ( sharab ( fazeekh pilaa raha tha aur main hi unmein sabse kam sun tha, itney mein aik shakhs aaya aur kaha : sharab haram kar di gaee hai. to (un ( logon ne kaha : Anas ! usko baha do. maine wo sab baha di. ( Sulaiman Taimi ne) kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : wo kya tha (jis se sharab banai gaee thi? ( unhon-ne kaha : wo kachchi aur pakkii khajoorein thin (Taimi ne) kaha : Abu-Bakar bin Anas ne kaha : un dinon yahi unki sharab thi. Sulaiman ne kaha : mujhey aik shakhs ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat bayan ki ke khud unhon-ne ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne bhi yahi kaha tha."
5134,"Muhammad-bin Abdul-Aala ne kaha : hamein Motamir (bin Sulaiman Taimi) ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki kaha : Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main khada hua qabeeley (ke logon) ko sharab pila raha tha, ibne-Ulaih ki riwayat ki tarah albatta unhon-ne (Motamir) ne kaha : Abu-Bakar bin Anas ne bataya un dinon unki sharab yahi thi aur us waqt Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) khud bhi) maujood they aur unhon-ne uska inkar nahi kya. (Sulaiman ne kaha :) aur jo log mere sath they unmein se aik shakhs ne kaha is ne ( khud ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna un dinon unki sharab yahi thi."
5135,"Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : main Ansari ki aik jama'iyat mein Hazrat abu Talha, Hazrat Abu dujana aur Hazrat Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ko sharab pila raha tha, us waqt aik aaney wala shakhs aaya aur kaha : sharab ki hurmat nazil ho gaee hai, (ye suntey hi) ham ne isi din usey (sharab ko) baha diya, wo neem pukhta aur khushk khajooron ki (bani hui) sharab thi. Qatada ne bataya ke Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : sharab haram kar di gaee aur un dinon aam taur par unki sharab mili-juli, neem pukhta aur khushk khajoor ki (bani hui) hoti thi."
5136,"Muaz ke walid Hisham ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : main Hazrat abu Talha, Hazrat abu Dujana aur Hazrat Suhel bin baiza (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ko aik mishkeezey se sharab pila raha tha, mili juli neem pukhta aur khushk khajooron ki sharab thi, jis tarah Saeed (bin abi-Aruba) ki hadis hai."
5137,"Amr-bin-Haris ne kaha ke Qatada bin Daama ne unhein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is baat se mana farmaya ke kachchi aur neem pukhta khajooron ka khaleet (pani mila ras ( banaya jaey, phir (is mein Khamer uthney ke baad) usey piya jaey aur jis din sharab haram hui us zamaney mein unki aam sharab yahi hua karti thi."
5138,"Ishaq bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha ne Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : main Hazrat abu Ubaida-bin jarrah, Hazrat abu Talha aur Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ko neem pukhta aur khushk khajooron ki (bani hui) sharab pila raha tha, us waqt unke paas aaney wala aik shakhs aaya aur kaha : sharab haram kar di gaee hai. Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Anas ! ja kar us ghadey ko tod do, maine apna peesney wala patthar (haawan dasta) uthaya aur uske nichley hissey ko us ghadey par maara yahan tak ke wo toot gaya."
5139,"abdul-hameed bin Jafar ne hamein apne walid se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey mere walid ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : jab Allah Taala ne wo aayat nazil farmai jis mein us ne sharab ko haram kya to us waqt Madina mein khajoor ke ilawa aur (kisi cheez ki bani hui) sharab nahi pi jati thi."
5140,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sharab ko sirka banaaney ke mutaalliq sawal kya gaya to aap ne farmaya : nahi.
5141,"Hazrat tariq bin Suwed jaufi (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sharab ( banaaney (ke mutaalliq sawal kya, aap ne us se mana farmaya ya iske banaaney ko na-pasand farmaya, unhon-ne kaha : main usko dawa ke liye banata hUn, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye dawa nahi hai, balke khud bimari hai."
5142,"Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne kaha ke abu Kasir ne unhein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : sharab un 2 darakhton (ke phalon) se banai jati hai. : khajoor aur angoor se."
5143,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : Auzai ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abu Kasir ne hadis sunai, kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna : aap farma rahe they : sharab un 2 darakhton (ke phalon) se taiyaar hoti hai : khajoor se aur angoor se."
5144,"Zuhair-bin-Harab aur abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein Wakee ne Auzai, Ikrima bin Ammar aur Aqba bin to-am se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Kaseer se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : sharab un 2 darakhton se banai jati hai : angoor ki bail aur khajoor ke darakht (ke phal ( se. abu-Kuraib ki riwayat mein) الْكَرْمَۃ وَالنَّخْلَۃ ki bajaey) الكرم والنخل ( hai. ( mafhoom aik hi hai.)"
5145,"Jareer-bin-Haazim ne kaha : maine Ata ibne-abi Ribah se suna, kaha : hamein Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khajooron aur kishmish aur kachchi khajooron aur pukhta khajooron ko mila kar mashroob banaaney se mana farmaya, (kyonke thodi hi der mein iska Khumair uth jata hai aur ye sharab mein tabdeel ho jata hai.)"
5146,"Leis ne ata ibne-abi Ribah se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khajooron aur kishmish ko mila kar nabeez banaaney se mana farmaya aur taaza khajooron aur kachchi khajooron ko mila kar nabeez banaaney se mana farmaya."
5147,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : Ata ne mujh se kaha ke maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : taaza khajooron aur kachchi khajooron ko aur kishmish aur khushk khajooron ko nabeez banaaney ke liye aik doosrey ke sath na milaao."
5148,Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne is baat se mana farmaya ke kishmish aur pukhta khajooron ko mila kar nabeez banaya jaey aur kachchi aur taaza khajooron ko mila kar nabeez banaya jaey.
5149,"Taimi ne abu-Nazara se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (nabeez banatey huey) khushk khajooron aur kishmish ko milaaney se aur pukhta khajooron aur kachchi khajooron ko milaaney se mana farmaya."
5150,"Saeed bin Yazeed abu-Muslima ne abu-Nazara se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is baat se mana farmaya ke ham (nabeez banaaney ke liye) kishmish aur khushk khajooron ko aik doosrey se mila dein aur kachchi aur khushk khajooron ko aapasi yakja kar lein."
5151,Bashar-bin-Mufazzal ne abu-Muslima se isi sanad ke sath usi ke manind riwaayat ki.
5152,"Wakee ne Ismail bin Muslim abdi se, unhon-ne abu mutawakkil naaji se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se jo shakhs nabeez piye wo sirf kishmish ka nabeez piye ya sirf khushk khajooron ka nabeez piye ya sirf kachchi khajooron ka nabeez piye."
5153,"Rooh bin Ubada ne kaha : hamein Ismail bin Muslim abdi ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein (nabeez mein) kachchi khajooron ko khushk khajooron ke sath milaaney, ya kishmish ko khushk khajoor ke sath ya kishmish ko neem pukhta khajooron ke sath milaaney se mana kya aur ye farmaya : tum mein se jo shakhs usey piye. aagey Wakee ki hadis ( 5152 ( ki tarah bayan kya."
5154,"Hisham dustwaai ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai Qatada se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : adh-pakki khajooron aur pakki khajooron ko milaakar nabeez na banao aur kishmish aur khushk khajooron ko mila kar nabeez na banao aur donon mein se har aik ki alag alag nabeez banao."
5155,Hajjaj-bin abi Usman ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5156,Ali-bin-Mubarak ne Yahya (bin abi kaseer) se unhon-ne abu-Salma se unhon-ne Hazrat abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : neem pukhta aur pukhta khajooron ko mila kar nabeez na banao aur taaza khajooron aur kishmish ko mila kar nabeez na banao albatta har jins ki alag-alag nabeez banao. Yahya ne ye bhi bataya ke unki Abdullah-bin-Ubai Qatada se mulaqat hui to unhon-ne apne walid se aur unke walid ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5157,"Husain muallim ne kaha : Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne hamein unhi donon sanadon se hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne kaha : taaza khajoor aur rang badalti khajoor khushk khajoor aur kishmish ki (nabeez na banao)"
5158,Aban Attar ne kaha : hamein Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne hadis bayan ki kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin-Ubai Qatada ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (nabeez banaaney ke liye) khushk badalti aur taaza khajooron ko aur rang badalti aur taaza khajooron ko milaaney se mana kya aur farmaya : har jins ki alag-alag nabeez banao.
5159,abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi sanad ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
5160,"Wakee ne Ikrima bin Ammar se unhon-ne abu Kasir hanfi se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kishmish aur khajooron kachchi aur khushk khajooron (ko mila kar nabeez banaaney) se mana kya aur farmaya : un donon mein se har aik ki alag alag nabeez banai jaey."
5161,"Hashim-bin-Qasim ne kaha : hamein Ikrima bin Ammar ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Yazeed bin Abdur-Rehman bin Azina ne aur wo Abu Kasir Anbari hain. hadis bayan ki kaha : mujhey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya usi ki tarah."
5162,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne hamein Shebani se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Habib se unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (nabeez banaaney ke liye) khushk khajooron aur kishmish ko aapas mein milaaney aur kachchi aur khushk khajooron ko aapas mein milaaney se mana farmaya aur aap ne ahale-Jurash ki taraf likha aur is baat se mana kya ke wo khushk khajooron aur kishmish ko mila kar mashroob banaaein."
5163,Khalid Tahan ne Shebani se isi sanad ke sath khushk khajooron aur kishmish ke mutaalliq riwayat bayan ki aur unhon-ne kachchi khajooron aur khushk khajooron ka zikr nahi kya.
5164,"Abdur-Razzaq ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di kaha : mujhey Musa-bin-Aqba ne bataya unhon-ne Naafe se unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ke wo kaha kartey they : kachchi aur taaza khajooron ko mila kar aur khushk khajooron aur kishmish ko mila kar nabeez banaaney se mana kar diya gaya."
5165,"Rooh ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Musa-bin-Aqba ne Naafe se khabar di unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : kachchi aur taaza khajooron ko aur (usi tarah) khushk khajooron aur kishmish ko mila kar nabeez banaaney se mana kya gaya hai."
5166,"Leis ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne unko bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kadu (ke baney huey) aur roghan zuft miley huey bartanon mein nabeez banaaney se mana farmaya."
5167,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kadu (ke baney huey) aur raughane-zuft miley huey bartanon mein nabeez banaaney se mana farmaya."
5168,"(guzishta sanad se riwayat kartey huey Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne) kaha : unhein abu-Salma ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kadu ke) baney huey) bartan mein nabeez na banao aur na raughane-zuft miley huey bartan mein. phir Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ye kehtey they : sabz ghadon se ijtinab karo."
5169,"Suhel ke walid ( Abu-Saleh ( ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne raughane-zuft miley huey bartanon, sabz ghadon aur khokhli (ki hui) lakdi ke bartanon se mana farmaya, (Abu-Saleh ne) kaha : Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha gaya ke hantam kya hai? unhon-ne bataya : sabz ( rang ke) ghadey."
5170,"Muhammad ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abdul-Qais ke wafad se farmaya : main tum ko kadu ke (baney huey) bartanon, hantam, khokhli lakdi ke bartanon, raughan qaar miley huey bartanon se mana karta hun. hantam wo mishkeezey hain jinke munh katey huey hun. lekin apne mishkezon se piyo aur unka munh baandh diya karo."
5171,"Abshar, Jarir aur Shoba sab ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Ibrahim Taimi se, unhon-ne Haris bin Suwed se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kadu ke baney huey aur raughane-zuft miley huey bartanon mein nabeez banaaney se mana farmaya, ye Jarir ki riwayat hai, absar aur Shoba ki hadis ke alfaz ye hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kadu ke) baney huey) bartan aur raughane-zuft miley bartan se mana farmaya hai."
5172,"Mansoor ne Ibrahim se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Aswad se kaha : kya tum ne Ummul-Momenin ( Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ( se un bartanon ke barey mein puchha tha jin mein nabeez banaana makruh hai? unhon-ne kaha : haan, maine kaha thi : Ummul-Momenin ! mujhey bataiye ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kin bartanon mein nabeez banaaney se mana farmaya tha? (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) farmaya : aap ne ham ahal bait ko kadu ke baney huey aur raughane-zuft miley huey bartanon mein nabeez banaaney se mana farmaya tha. ( Ibrahim ne) kaha : maine ( Aswad se) puchha : unhon-ne hantam aur ghadon ka zikr nahi kiya? unhon-ne kaha : main tum ko wahi hadis bayan karta hun jo maine suni hai. kya main tumhen wo baat bayan karun jo maine nahi suni?"
5173,"Aamash ne Ibrahim se unhon-ne Aswad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kadu ke baney huey aur roghane-zuft miley huey bartanon se mana farmaya,"
5174,"Mansoor, Sulaiman aur Hammad ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Aswad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
5175,"Samama bin huzn qushairi ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein haziri di to maine unse nabeez ke mutaalliq sawal kya, unhon-ne mujhey hadis sunai ke (banu-) abdul-Qais ka wafad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se nabeez ke mutaalliq sawal kya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko kadu ke) baney huey) bartan , khokhli lakdi ke bartanon, raughane-zuft miley huey bartanon aur sabz ghadon mein nabeez banaaney se mana farmaya."
5176,"ibne-Ulaih ne kaha : hamein Ishaq bin Suwed ne Muaza se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kadu ke) baney huey) bartan, sabz ghadon, khokhli lakdi ke bartanon aur raughane-zuft miley huey bartanon ke istemal se mana farmaya."
5177,"Abdul-Wahaab Saqafi ne kaha : hamein Ishaq bin Suwed ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki magar unhon-ne raughane-zuft miley huey bartan ki bajaey muqeer (raughane-qaar mila bartan) bataya. ( donon se aik hi cheez , nabaataati tel murad hai.)"
5178,"Ibad bin Ibad aur Hammad-bin-Zaid ne abu Hamza se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein abdul-Qais ka wafad hazir hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main tum ko kadu ke) baney huey) bartanon, sabz ghadon, khokhli lakdi ke bartanon aur raughane-qaar miley huey bartanon (main nabeez banaaney aur peeney ( se mana karta hun. Hammad ne apni hadis mein muqeer ke bajaey muzaffat ka lafz bayan kya."
5179,"Habib bin abi Sabit ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khokhley kadu , sabz ghadon, raughane-zuft miley bartanon aur khokhli lakdi (ke bartanon) se mana farmaya,"
5180,"Habib-bin-abi Umra ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khokhley kadu, sabz ghadon, raughane-zuft miley huey bartanon (main nabeez banaaney ( se aur kachchi aur adh-paki pukhta khajooron ko (mashroob banatey huey aapas mein) milaaney se mana farmaya,"
5181,"Yahya bin abi umr ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kadu ke) baney huey) bartanon, khokhli lakdi aur raughane-zuft miley huey bartanon se mana farmaya."
5182,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghadon mein nabeez banaaney se mana farmaya.
5183,"Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba ne Qatada se, unhon-ne abu-Nazara se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khokhley kadu, sabz ghadon, khokhli lakdi aur raughane-zuft miley huey bartanon se mana farmaya."
5184,"Hisham ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (un bartanon mein) nabeez banaaney se mana farmaya, padhi. usi (pichhli riwayat) ki tarah bayan kya."
5185,"abu mutawakkil ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sabz ghadey , kadu ke (baney huey) bartan aur khokhli lakdi ke bartan main (nabeez bana kar) peeney se mana farmaya,"
5186,"Mansoor bin Hayyan ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se riwayat ki, kaha : main Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke mutaalliq shahadat deta hun ke un donon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke mutaalliq shahadat di ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kadu ke) baney huey) bartanon , sabz ghadon , raughane-zuft miley bartanon aur khokhli lakdi (ke bartanon ( se mana farmaya,"
5187,"Yala bin-Hakim ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se ghadon ki nabeez ke mutaalliq sawal kya, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghadon mein banai hui nabeez ko haram qarar diya hai. main Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya aur kaha : kaha aap ne nahi suna ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) kya farmatey hain? unhon-ne kaha : wo kya kehtey hain? maine kaha : wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghadon mein nabeez banaaney ko haram kar diya hai. to unhon (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne sach kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghadon mein banai hui nabeez ko haram kar diya hai. maine puchha : ghadon ki nabeez se kya murad hai? unhon-ne kaha : har wo bartan jo mitti se banaya jaey. (is mein banai gaee nabeez.)"
5188,"Imam Malik (Rehmatullahi-alaih) Mina ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik ghazwey ke doran mein logon ko khutba diya. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka irshaad sunney ke liye) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf badha, lekin aap mere pahunchne se pahley (wahan se) tashrif ley gaey. maine puchha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya farmaaya? logon ne mujhey bataya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kadu ke bartan aur raughane-zuft lagey huey bartanon mein nabeez banaaney se mana farmaya."
5189,"Lais-bin-Sad, Ayub, Ubaidullah, Yahya-bin-Saeed, Suhak bin Usman aur Usama un sab ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se Malik ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki, Malik aur Usama ke siwa unmein se kisi ne aik ghazwey ke doran mein ke alfaz nahi kahey."
5190,"Sabit se riwayat hai, kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mitti ke ghadon ki nabeez se mana farmaya tha? Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : logon ne yahi kaha hai, maine kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us (qism ke ghadon ki nabeez) se mana farmaya tha? Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : logon ne yahi kaha hai."
5191,"Sulaiman Taimi ne Taaus se riwayat ki, kaha : aik shakhs ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghadon ki nabeez se mana farmaya tha? unhon-ne kaha : haan. phir Taaus ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se is tarah suna hai."
5192,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey ibne-Taaus ne apne walid se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs unke paas aaya aur puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mitti ke ghadon aur kadu ke) baney huey) bartan mein nabeez banaaney se mana farmaya tha? unhon-ne kaha haan."
5193,"Wuhaib ne Abdullah-bin Taaus se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mitti ke ghadon aur kadu ke) baney huey) bartan mein nabeez banaaney se mana farmaya tha."
5194,"Ibrahim bin Maisra se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Taaus ko ye kehtey huey suna : main Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas betha hua tha ke aik shakhs ne aa kar unse puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghadon , kadu ke bartan aur zuft miley huey bartan mein bani hui nabeez se mana farmaya tha? unhon-ne farmaya : haan."
5195,"Shoba ne Maharib bin Disaar se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sabz ghadon aur kadu ke) baney huey) bartan aur raughane-zuft miley huey bartan mein nabeez banaaney se mana farmaya tha aur (Maharib bin Disaar ne) kaha : maine ye ( hadis) unse aik se zyada baar suni."
5196,"Shebani ne Maharib bin Disaar se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki. ( Shebani ne) kaha : aur mera guman hai) Maharib ne) khokhli lakdi ka bhi zikr kya."
5197,"Aqba bin Hurais ne kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mitti ke ghadey, kadu ke (baney huey) bartan aur raughane-zuft miley huey bartanon se mana kya aur farmaya : mishkezon mein nabeez banao."
5198,"jabla ne kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko hadis bayan kartey huey suna, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hantama se mana farmaya ( jabla ne) kaha : maine puchha : hantama kya hai? ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : ghada."
5199,"Ubaidullah ke walid Muaz ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Amr-bin-Murra se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Zazan ne hadis bayan ki kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke peeney ki chizon ke hawale se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jin chizon se mana kya hai unke mutaalliq mujhey (pahley) apni zaban mein hadis sunain phir hamari zaban mein uski wazaahat karein kyonke aap ki zaban hamari zaban se mukhtalif hai. unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hantam se aur wo ghada hai aur dubba se aur wo kadu hai aur muzaffat se aur wo raughan qaar mila hua bartan hai aur naqeer se aur wo khajoor ka tana hai usey chhila jata hai aur usko kureda jata hai mana farmaya hai aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ke mishkezon mein nabeez banai jaey."
5200,Abu-Dawud ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki.
5201,"Abdul-Khaliq bin Salma ne kaha : maine Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ko kehtey huey suna ke maine Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko us member ke paas kehtey huey suna aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke member ki taraf ishara kya : qabila abd-al-qais ka wafad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se peeney ki chizon ke hawale se sawal kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein kadu se baney huey bartan andar se kuredi hui lakdi ke bartan aur sabz ghadey se mana farmaya, (Abdul-Khaliq bin Salma ne kaha) maine kaha : abu-Muhammad! aur raughane-zuft mila hua bartan? ham ne samjha tha ke wo iska zikr karna bhool gaey hain. to unhon (Saeed-bin-Musaiyab) ne kaha : maine us din Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se ye (muzaffat ka zikr) nahi suna tha. wo usko ( bhi) na-pasand kartey they."
5202,"abu khaisma ( Zuhair ( ne abu-Zubair se unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir aur Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne lakdi ke bartan raughane-zuft miley huey bartan aur kadu ke bartan se mana farmaya."
5203,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna : aap ghadon, kadu aur raughane-zuft miley huey bartanon se mana farma rahe they."
5204,"abu-Zubair ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghadon raughane-zuft miley huey bartan aur lakdi ke bartan se mana farmaya, (aur ( jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan nabeez banaaney ke liye koi aur bartan na milta to pattharon se baney huey badey bartan mein aap ke liye nabeez banai jati."
5205,"abu-Awana ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye pattharon se baney huey aik badey bartan mein nabeez banai jati thi."
5206,"hamein abu khaisma ( Zuhair) ne abu-Zubair se khabar di unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye aik mishkeezey mein nabeez banai jati thi aur jab mishkeeza na milta to pattharon se baney huey aik badey bartan mein nabeez banai jati thi. logon mein se aik shakhs ne abu-Zubair se kaha : aur main sun raha tha. padhi. mazbut patthar se bana hua? kaha : ( haan) mazbut patthar se bana hua."
5207,"Zarar bin Murra abu Sanan ne Maharib bin Disaar se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Barida se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine tum logon ko mashk ke siwa doosrey bartanon mein nabeez banaaney se mana kya tha (ab tum log) sab bartanon mein piyo lekin koi nasha aawar cheez na piyo."
5208,Alqama bin-Marsad ne ibne-bareeda se unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine tum ko kuchh bartanon se mana kya tha bartan kisi cheez ko halal kartey hain na haram albatta har nasha aawar cheez haram hai.
5209,"moarrif bin Wasil ne Maharib bin Disaar se unhon-ne ibne-bareeda se unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine tum ko chamdey ke bartanon mein mashroobaat ( peeney ( se mana kya tha. ( ab (har bartan mein piyo magar koi nasha aawar cheez na piyo ."
5210,Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( kuchh khas ( bartanon mein nabeez ( banaaney ( se mana farmaya (aur mishkezon mein mashroob banaaney aur peeney ka hukm diyaa) to logon ne kaha : har shakhs ko) mishkeezey ya doosrey bartan ( muyassar nahi hotey is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mitti ke aisey ghadon ki ijazat di jis mein raughane-zuft mila hua na ho.
5211,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se shehad ki bani hui sharab ke mutaalliq sawal kya gaya aap ne farmaya : har mashroob jo nasha aawar ho wo haram hai."
5212,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko kehtey huey suna, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se shehad ki bani hui sharab ke mutaalliq sawal kya gaya to aap ne farmaya : har mashroob jo nasha aawar ho wo haram hai."
5213,(Sufiyan) ibne-Uena Saleh aur Mamar sab ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki Sufiyan aur Saleh ki hadis main ye (alfaz) nahi ke aap se shehad ki bani hui sharab ke barey mein puchha gaya ye alfaz Mamar ki hadis mein hain. Saleh ki hadis mein hai unhon-ne (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : har nasha aawar mashroob haram hai.
5214,"Shoba ne Saeed bin abi burda se unhon-ne apne walid se unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey aur Hazrat Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yaman ki taraf bheja maine kaha ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! hamarey ilaaqey mein jo se aik mashroob banaya jata hai usko Muzar kehtey hain aur aik mashroob shehad se banaya jata hai usko Bita kehtey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har nasha aawar cheez haram hai."
5215,Amr ne Sad bin abi Burda se suna unhon-ne apne walid ( abu-Burda Aamir bin abi Musa (ke waastey se apne dada se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko aur Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yaman bheja aur farmaya : tum donon logon ko) achchhey aamaal ke inaam ki) khush khabri sunana aur (maamlaat ko) aasan banaana (deen) seekhaana aur mutnaffar na karna mera khayal hai ke unhon-ne ye bhi riwayat kya aap ne farmaya : donon aik doosrey se muwafiqat se rehna. jab ( ijazat lekar ( abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) peechhey ki taraf mudey to kaha : Allah ke rasool! unka shehad se banaya ho aik mashroob hai jisey pakaaya jata hai yahan tak ke wo gaadha ho jata hai aur (eik mashroob ( Muzar hai jisey jo se taiyaar kya jata hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har wo cheez jo Namaz se madhosh kar de wo haram hai.
5216,"Zaid-bin-abii-Unaisa ne Saeed bin abi Burda se riwayat ki, kaha : hamein Hazrat abu-Burda ne apne walid se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey aur Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yaman ki taraf bheja aap ne farmaya : logon ko (Islam ki) dawat dena unko khushkhabri dena aur mutnaffar na karna. maamlaat ko aasan banaana aur logon ko mushkil mein na daalna. unhon-ne kaha : maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! ham ko 2 mashroobon ke barey mein shariiat ka hukm bataiye jinhein ham Yaman mein taiyaar kartey they. aik bitaa hai jo shehad se taiyaar kya jata hai. usey bartanon mein daala jata hai yahan tak ki wo gaadha ho jata hai aur aik Muzar hai wo makai aur jo se taiyaar kya jata hai usey bartanon mein daala jata hai yahan tak ke usmein shiddat paida ho jati hai. unhon-ne kaha : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko baat ke khoobsurat khaatmey samet jaame kalimaat ata kiye gaey they. aap ne farmaya : main har us nasha aawar cheez se mana karta hun jo Namaz se madhosh kar de. ( jiski zyada miqdar madhosh kar de uski qaleel tareen miqdar bhi haram hai.)"
5217,abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs Jaishan se aaya Jaishan Yaman mein hai us ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se apni sar zamin ke aik mashroob ke mutaalliq sawal kya jis ko makai se banaya jata tha iska naam Muzar tha Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : kya wo nasha aawar hai? usne kaha : ji haan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har nasha aawar cheez haram hai bila shubah izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ka (apne uper ye ( ahad hai ke jo shakhs nasha aawar mashroob piyega wo usko teenatul-Khabal pilaaeyga. sahaba ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! teenatul-Khabal kya hai? aap ne farmaya : jahannamiyon ka paseena ya (farmaya : ( jahannamiyon ka nichod.
5218,Ayub ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki : kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har nasha aawar cheez khumr hai aur har nasha aawar cheez haram hai aur jis shakhs ne duniya mein sharab pi aur us haalat mein mar gaya ke wo sharab ka aadi ho gaya tha aur us ne tauba nahi ki thi to wo aakhirat mein usey nahi piyega.
5219,ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Musa-bin-Aqba ne Naafe se khabar di unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har nasha aawar cheez khumr hai aur nasha aawar cheez haram hai.
5220,Abdul-Azeez bin Muttalib ne Musa-bin-Aqba se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5221,"Ubaidullah ne kaha : hamein Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, kaha : is baat ka ilm mujh ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hi ki taraf se hai ke aap ne farmaya : har nasha-aawar cheez khumr hai aur har khumr haram hai."
5222,Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : maine Imam Malik ke samney qirat ki ke Naafe se riwayat hai unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne duniya mein sharab pi wo aakhirat mein us se mahroom rahega.
5223,"Abdullaah-bin-Muslima bin Qanab ne kaha : hamein Malik ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki, (unhon-ne) Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jis shakhs ne duniya mein sharab pi aur us se tauba nahi ki usey aakhirat mein us se mehroom kar diya jaeyga wo usey nahi pilaai jaeygi. Imam Malik se puchha gaya : kya unhon-ne (hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kiya? unhon-ne kaha : haan."
5224,"Ubaidullah ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne duniya mein sharab pi wo aakhirat mein nahi piyega. siwaey-iske ke wo tauba kar ley."
5225,"Musa-bin-Aqba ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Ubaidullah ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
5226,Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Yahya bin Ubaid abu umr bahraani se riwayat bayan ki kaha : maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye raat ke shuruaati hissey main ( khajooren (pani mein daal di jati thin jab aap subah kartey to usey ( peetey (aur jo raat aati (is mein) peetey aur subah ko aur agli raat ko iske baad ka din Asr tak agar kuchh bach jata to khaadim ko pilaa detey (taake khatm ho jaey) ya (agar koi peeney wala na hota ya bach jati to ( usko gira dene ka hukm detey.
5227,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Yahya behrani se hadis bayan ki, kaha : logon ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney nabeez ka zikr kya to unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye pair ki raat ko mishkeezey main (pani ke sath khajoor daal kar) nabeez bana li jati thi to aap usey pair ko aur mangal ko Asr tak peetey agar usmein se kuchh bach jata to khaadim ko pila detey ya gira detey."
5228,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se unhon-ne abu umr se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye kishmish ko pani mein daal diya jata aap us nabeez ko us din aur us se agley din aur uske baad waley teesrey din ki Sham (Syria) tak nosh farmatey, phir aap hukm detey to wo dusron ko pilaa di jati thi ya gira di jati thi."
5229,"Jarir ne Aamash se unhon-ne Yahya abu umr se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye mashk mein kishmish daal di jati thi aap usko us din peetey aur uske agley din aur uske baad waley din tak peetey aur jab teesrey din ki Sham (Syria) hoti to aap usko khud peetey kisi aur ko pilaatey phir agar bach jata to usko baha detey."
5230,"Zaid ne abu umr Yahya Nakhai se riwayat ki kaha : kuchh logon ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se sharab bechney kharidney aur uski tijarat ke mutaalliq sawal kya. to unhon-ne puchha : kya tum log musalman ho? unhon-ne kaha : haan. Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : sharab ka bechna khareedna aur uski tijarat karna jaaiz nahi hai. phir unhon-ne nabeez ke mutaalliq sawal kya. Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik safar par tashrif le gaey phir aap ki waapsi hui. aap ke sathiyon ne sabz ghadon, kuredi hui lakdi aur kadu ke bartanon mein nabeez banai hui thi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey gira deney ka hukm diya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik mishkeeza laney ka hukm diya usmein kishmish aur pani daal diye gaey ye ( nabeez (raat ko banai gaee Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne subah ki to us din usko piyaa agli raat ko piya phir agley din Sham (Syria) tak piya, piya aur pilaya jab agli subah hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jo bach gaya tha iske barey mein hukm diya to usey gira diya gaya."
5231,"hamein Samama yani ibne- huzn qushairi ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se milney gaya to maine unse nabeez ke mutaalliq sawal kya, Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne aik habshi kaneez ko awaz di aur farmaya is se poochho yahi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye nabeez banaya karti thi. us habshi ladki ne kaha : main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye raat ko aik mashk main ( phal ( daal deti thi aur us mashk ka munh baandh kar usko latka deti thi jab subah hoti to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usmein se nosh farmatey they."
5232,"Hasan ki walida ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye aik mashk mein nabeez banatey iska uper ka hissa baandh diya jata tha usmein nichli taraf ka suraakh bhi tha. ham subah ko) khajoor ya kishmish ( daltey to aap usey raat ko nosh farmatey aur raat ke waqt daltey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ko nosh farmatey."
5233,"Abdul-Azeez bin abi Hazim ne abu-Hazim se unhon-ne Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat abu Usaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni shadi main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dawat di us din unki biwi khidmat bajaa la rahi thin, halanke wo dulhan thin. Sehal ne kaha : kya tum jantey ho ke usne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kya pilaya tha? us ne raat ko patthar ke aik badey bartan mein pani ke andar kuchh khajoorein daal di thin jab aap khaney se farigh huey to usne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wo ( mashroob ( pilaya ."
5234,"Yaqoob bin Abdur-Rehman ne abu-Hazim se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se suna keh rahe they Hazrat abu Usaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dawat di. usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah . unhon-ne ye nahi kaha, jab aap ne khana tanaawul farma liya us ne wo ( mashroob ( aapko pilaya."
5235,"Muhammad Abu-Ghassan ne kaha : mujhey abu-Hazim ne Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se yahi hadis riwayat ki aur kaha : (is ne) patthar ke aik badey piyaa ley main ( nabeez banai ( phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khaney se farigh huey to us ( abu Usaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ki dulhan ( ne us ( phal ko jo pani ke sath bartan mein daala hua tha) pani mein ghulaaya aur aapko pilaya, aapko khususi taur par (pilaya.)"
5236,"Muhammad-bin-Sahal-Taimi aur Abu-Bakar-bin-Ishaq ne kaha : hamein ibne-abi-Maryam ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abu-Ghassan-Muhammad-bin-Mutrif ne bataya ke mujhey abu-Hazim ne Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat bayan ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney Arab ki aik aurat ka zikr kiya gaya. (uske walid Nauman-bin-abi-jon-kindi ne pesh kaash! ki) aap ne abu Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : ke us (aurat ko la ne ke liye us) ki taraf sawari wghaira bhejin . to unhon (Hazrat abu Usaid (Raziallahu anhu)) ne bhej di wo aurat aai banu- saaida ke qile' numaa makanon mein thehri. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghar se rawaana ho kar uske paas tashrif le gaey jab aap uske paas gaey to wo aurat sar jhukaae huey thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab us se baat ki to wo kehney lagi : main aap se Allah ki panah mein aati hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine tumhen khud se panah de di. logon ne us se kaha : kya tum janti ho ye kon hain? usne kaha : nahi unhon-ne kaha : ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) they aur tumhen nikah ka paigham dene tumharey paas aaey they. usne kaha : main us se kam tar naseeb wali thi. Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha is din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aap khud aur aap ke sathi banu-saaida ke chhat waley chabootrey par tashrif farma huey, phir Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : pani pilaaw kaha : maine unke liye wahi piyala (numaa bartan) nikala aur is mein aapko pilaya . abu-Hazim ne kaha : Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamarey liye bhi wahi piyala nikala aur ham ne bhi usmein se piyaa. phir Umar-bin-Abdul Azeez ne Hazrat Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) se wo piyala bataur hiba maang liya. Hazrat Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne wo piyala unko hiba kar diya Abu-Bakar-bin-Ishaq ki riwayat mein hai : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Sehal ! hamein (kuchh) pilaaw."
5237,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke maine apne us piyaley se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko har qisam ka mashroob pilaya hai. shahad, nabeez, pani aur doodh."
5238,"Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Abu-Ishaq (Hamdani) se hadis bayan ki. unhon-ne Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke jab ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Makka se Madina ki taraf rawaana huey to ham aik charwaahey ke paas se guzrey. us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko piyaas lagi hui thi. unhon (Hazrat Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye kuchh doodh dohaa, phir main aap ke paas wo doodh laya , aap ne usey nosh farmaya, yahan tak ke main razi ho gaya."
5239,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Abu-Ishaq Hamdani se suna, keh rahe they : maine Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka se Madina ko aaey to suraaqa-bin-Malik ne (mushrikon ki taraf se) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka peechhaa kiya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske liye baddua ki to uska ghoda (zameen mein) dhans gaya (yani zamin ne usko pakad liya). wo bola ke aap mere liye dua kijiye mein aapko nuqsan nahi pahunchaaunga. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Allah se dua ki (to usko nijat mili) phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko piyaas lagi aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bakriyon ke charwaahey ke qareeb se guzrey. saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine piyala liya aur thoda sa doodh Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye dohaa aur lekar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne piyaa , yahan tak ke main khush ho gaya."
5240,"Yunus ne Zohri se riwayat ki, kaha : ibne-Musaiyab ne kaha : Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jis raat baitul-maqdis ki sair karaai gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas do piyaley laey gaey. aik mein sharab thi aur aik mein doodh , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne donon ko dekha aur doodh ka piyala ley liya. Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke shukr hai us Allah ka jisne aapko fitrat ki hidayat ki (yani Islam ki aur istiqaamat ki) . agar aap sharab ko letey to aap ki ummat gumrah ho jati."
5241,"Maaqil ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas (do piyaley) laey gaey, usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah . unhon (Maaqil) ne eliyaa ka zikr nahi kiya."
5242,"abu-Aasim Suhak ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : mujh se abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik piyala doodh ka (maqam) naqeea' se laya. jo dhaanpaa hua na tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tu ney usko dhaanpaa kyon nahi? (agar dhaanpney ko kuchh na tha to) aik aadi lakdi hi is par rakh leta . abu-Humed ( rawi hadis) kehtey hain ke hamein raat ke waqt mishkezon ko baandhney aur darwazey band karne ka hukm farmaya."
5243,"Rooh-bin-Ubada ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij aur Zakariya-bin-Ishaq ne hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : mujhey Hazrat abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas doodh ka aik piyala laaey, usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah . Zakariya ne (apni riwayat ki hui hadis mein) Hazrat abu-Humaid (Raziallahu anhu) ka qaul : raat ke waqt bayan nahi kiya."
5244,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they ke aap ne pani maanga, aik shakhs ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko nabeez na pilaaein? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kyon nahi ! phir wo shakhs daudta hua gaya aur aik piyaley mein nabeez lekar aaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ne isey dhaank kar kyon nahi diya? chahey tum iske uper chaudai ke rukh aik lakdi (hi) rakh detey. (Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nosh farmaya."
5245,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Sufiyan Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik shakhs jo abu Humaid kehlata tha, naqeea' ( maqam se) se doodh ka aik piyala laya. jo dhaanpa hua na tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tu ney usko dhaanpa kyon nahi ? (agar dhaanpney ko kuchh na tha to ( chahey tum iske uper chaudai ke rukh aik lakdi (hi) rakh detey."
5246,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin Rumeh ne Leis se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bartanon ko dhaank do, mashkon ka munh band kar do, darwaza band kar do, aur charagh bujhaa do, kyonke shaitan mishkeezey ka munh nahi kholtaa , wo darwaza (bhi) nahi kholtaa , kisi bartan ko bhi nahi kholtaa hai. agar tum mein se kisi ko uskey siwa aur cheez na miley ke wo apne bartan par chaudai ke bal lakdi hi rakh de, ya is par Allah ka naam ( bismillaah ( padh de to (yahi) kar ley kyonke chuhiyaa ghar walon ke uper (yani jab wo uski chhat taley soey hotey hain) unka ghar jalaa deti hai. Quteba ne apni hadis mein : aur darwaza band kar do ke alfaz bayan nahi kiye."
5247,"Imam Malik (Rehmatullahi-alaih) ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis riwayat ki, magar unhon-ne (yun) kaha : bartan ulat kar rakh do ya unhein dhaank do aur bartan par chaudai ke rukh lakdi rakhney ka zikr nahi kiya."
5248,"Zuhair ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : darwaza band kar do phir Leis ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya, albatta unhon-ne kaha : aur bartanon ko dhaank do aur ye kaha : wo (chuhiyaa) ghar walon par unke kapdey jalaa deti hai."
5249,"Sufiyan ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se unki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki aur farmaya : chuhiyaa ghar walon ke uper ghar ko jalaa deti hai."
5250,"Ishaq-bin-Mansur ne kaha : hamein Rooh-bin-Ubada ne khabar di kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Ata ne bataya ke unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab raat ho jaey ya farmaya ke tum Sham karo to apne bachchon ko (gharon mein) rok lo. kyonke us waqt shaitan phail jatey hain. phir jab kuchh raat guzar jaey to bachchon ko chhod do aur Allah ka naam ley darwazey band kar do. kyonke shaitan band darwazey nahi kholtaa aur Allah ka naam lekar apne mishkezon ka bandhan baandh do aur apne bartanon ko dhaank lo Allah ka naam lekar . (agar bartan dhaankney ke liye aur kuchh na miley siwa iske ( un bartanon ke uper koi cheez chaudai mein rakho (to wahi rakh do (aur apne charaaghon ko bujhaa do."
5251,"Ishaq-bin-Mansur ne kaha : hamein Rooh-bin-Ubada ne khabar di, kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne hadis bayan ki, kaha mujhey Amr-bin-Dinar ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo is tarah keh rahe they jis tarah Ata ne bataya, albatta unhon-ne ye nahi kaha : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ka naam lo."
5252,abu-Aasim ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne yahi hadis ata aur Amr-bin-Dinar se Rooh ki riwayat ki tarah bayan ki.
5253,"abu khaisma (Zuhair) ne abu-Zubair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : suraj ghurub honey lagey to apne phail janey waley janwaron aur bachchon ko bahar na bhejo yahan tak ke isha ki aamad ka andhera rukhsat ho jaey, kyonke suraj ghurub honey ke baad isha ki aamad ka andhera khatm honey tak shaitanon ko chhoda jata hai."
5254,"Sufiyan bin-abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Zuhair ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
5255,"Hashim-bin-Qasim ne kaha : hamein Lais-bin-Sad ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Yazeed-bin-Abdullah-bin-Usama-bin-haad Lesi ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne Jafar-bin-Abdullah-bin-hukm se, unhon-ne qa'qa'-bin-Hakim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : bartan dhaank do, mishkeezey ka munh baandh do, kyonke saal mein aik raat aisi hoti hai jis mein wabaa nazil hoti hai. phir jis bhi bina dhakey bartan aur munh khuley mishkeezey ke paas se guzarti hai. to us wabaa mein se (kuchh hissa) usmein utar jata hai."
5256,Ali jahazmi ne kaha : hamein Lais-bin-Sad ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki magar unhon-ne us ( hadis) mein ye kaha saal mein aik aisa din hai jis mein wabaa nazil hoti hai. (Ali ne) hadis ke aakhir mein ye izafa kiya : Leis ne kaha : hamarey yahaan ke ajami log kanoon awwal (yani december) mein us wabaa se bachtey hain (bachney ke heeley kartey hain).
5257,"Salim ne apne walid (Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab tum soney lago to apne gharon main ( jaltii hui ( aag na chhoda karo (usey poori tarah bujhaa diya karo)."
5258,"Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Madina mein aik ghar apne rehney walon ke uper jal gira. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko unka haal sunaya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye aag jo hai ye tumhari dushman hai. jab tum soney lago to usko khud se (hataaney ke liye) bujhaa diya karo."
5259,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne khaisma se, unhon-ne abu-Huzaifa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ke jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khana khaatey to apne hath na daltey jab tak Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) shuru na kartey aur hath na daaltey. aik baar ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khaney par maujood they aur aik ladki daudti hui aai jaisey koi usko haank raha hai aur us ne apna hath khaney mein dalna chaha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uska hath pakad liya. phir aik dehati daudta hua aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uska hath thaam liya. phir farmaya ke shaitan us khaney par qudrat pa leta hai jis par Allah Taala ka naam na liya jaey aur wo aik ladki ko us khaney par qudrat hasil karne ko laya to maine uska hath pakad liya, phir us dehati ko usi gharaz se laya to maine uska bhi hath pakad liya. qism uski jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! us (shaitan) ka hath us ladki ke hath ke sath mere hath mein hai."
5260,"Isa-bin-Yonus ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne khaisma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se khabar di, unhon-ne abu-Huzaifa-Arhabi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Huzaifa-bin-yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khaney ki dawat di jaati, phir abu-Muawia ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, aur kaha : jaisey us ( baddoo ( ko peechhey se zor se dhakelaa ja raha ho. aur ladki ke barey mein kaha : jaisey usey peechhey se zor se dhakelaa ja raha ho, unhon-ne apni hadis mein baddoo ke aaney ka zikr pahley kiya aur ladki ke aaney ka baad main aur hadis ke aakhir mein izafa kiya : phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bismillaah padhi aur khaya."
5261,"Sufiyan ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur ladki ka aana , dehati ke aaney se pahley bayan kiya."
5262,"abu-Aasim ne ibne-Juraij se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ke jab aadmi apne ghar mein jata hai, aur ghar mein dakhil hotey waqt aur khana khaatey waqt Allah jal jalaala ka naam leta hai, to shaitan (apne rafeeqon aur taabedaron se) kehta hai ke na tumharey yahan rehney ka thikana hai, na khana hai aur jab ghar mein dakhil hotey waqt Allah Taala ka naam nahi leta to shaitan kehta hai ke tumhen rehney ka thikana to mil gaya aur jab khaatey waqt bhi Allah Taala ka naam nahi leta to shaitan kehta hai ke tumharey rehney ka thikana bhi hua aur khana bhi mila."
5263,"Rooh-bin-Ubada ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna. unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna. abu-Aasim ki hadis ki tarah , albatta unhon-ne ye kaha : aur agar us ne apne khaney ke waqt Allah ka naam na liya aur agar us ne dakhil hotey waqt Allah ka naam na liya."
5264,Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : baain hath se na khaao kyonke shaitan baain hath se khata hai.
5265,"Sufiyan ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Abu-Bakar-bin-Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullah-bin-Umar se, unhon-ne apne dada Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs khana khaaey to apne daain hath se khaaey aur jab tum mein se koi shakhs piye to apne daain hath se piye kyonke shaitan baain hath se khata hai aur baain hath se peeta hai."
5266,Ubaidullah ne Zohri se Sufiyan ki sanad ke sath (hadis bayan ki).
5267,"abu-Taahir aur hurmula ne kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin-Wahab ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Umar-bin-Muhammad ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Qasim-bin-Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullah-bin-Umar ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Salim se, unhon-ne apne walid (hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs na baain hath se khaaey na us hath se piye kyonke shaitan baain hath se khata hai. aur usi se peetaa hai. Naafe is riwayat mein ye izafa kartey hain : na us (baain hath) se ley aur na uske zariey se de. aur abu-Taahir ki riwayat mein hai : tum mein se koi shakhs (baain hath se) hargiz na khaaey."
5268,"saiyedna Ayas-bin-Salma-bin-Akwa apne walid se riwayat kartey hain ke unhon-ne kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik shakhs ne baain hath se khaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke daain hath se kha . wo bola ke mere se nahi ho sakta. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah karey tujh se na ho sakey. us ne aisa ghurur ki raah se kiya tha. rawi kehta hai ke wo saari zindagi us hath ko munh tak na utha saka."
5269,"Waleed-bin-Kasir ne Wahab-bin-kaisaan se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Umar-bin-abi-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki god mein tha (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar mein parwarish pa raha tha) aur mera hath piyaley mein sab taraf ghoom raha tha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey ladkey : bismillaah padh kar daahiney hath se kha aur jo paas ho udhar se kha."
5270,"Muhammad-bin-Amr-bin-Halhala ne Wahab-bin-kaisaan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Umar-bin-abi-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : aik din maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khana khaya aur maine piyaley ke har taraf se gosht lena shuru kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apne aagey se khaao."
5271,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( munh laga kar peeney ke liye) mashkon ko ultaaney se mana farmaya."
5272,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mashkon ko ulatney se (yani seedhey-seedhey ( unke munh se pani peeney se mana farmaya hai."
5273,"Mamar ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki, albatta unhon-ne kaha : un (mashkon) ka ikhtinaas ye hai ke mashk ka munh ulat kar usmein se (seedhey-seedhey) pani piyaa jaey."
5274,"Hammam ne kaha : hamein Qatada ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khadey hokar pani peeney se daant kar mana farmaya."
5275,"Saeed ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne khadey ho kar pani peeney se mana farmaya, Qatada ne kaha : ham ne puchha aur (khadey ho kar) khana? to (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : ye zyada bura aur gandaa (tareeqa) hai."
5276,"Hisham ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki aur Qatada ka qaul zikr nahi kiya."
5277,"Hammam ne kaha : Qatada ne hamein abu Isa-ustwaari se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khadey ho kar pani peeney se daant kar roka."
5278,"Shoba ne kaha : hamein Qatada ne abu Isa-ustwaari se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khadey ho kar pani peeney se mana farmaya."
5279,"abu-Ghatfaan murri se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs khadey ho kar hargiz na piye aur jisne bhool kar khadey ho kar pi liya, wo qai kar de."
5280,"abu-Awana ne Aasim se, unhon-ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko zam-zam ka pani pilaya to aap ne khadey-khadey piyaa."
5281,"Sufiyan ne Aasim se, unhon-ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zam-zam ka pani , uske aik dol se khadey-khadey piyaa."
5282,"Hushaim ne kaha : hamein Aasim ahwal aur Mughira ne Shabi se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zam-zam ka pani piyaa jabke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey they."
5283,"Muaz ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Aasim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Shabi ko suna, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko zam-zam pilaya to aap ne khadey-khadey piyaa , aap ne (us waqt) pani maanga tha (jab (aap Baitullah ke paas they."
5284,Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur Wahab-bin-Jareer donon ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki. donon ki hadis mein hai : main dol lekar aap ke paas aaya.
5285,Abdullah-bin-Ubai Qatada ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is baat se mana farmaya hai ke bartan ke andar saans liya jaey.
5286,samaama-bin-Abdullah-bin-Anas ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bartan mein (se pani peetey huey us se munh hata kar) teen martaba saans letey they.
5287,"Abdul-Waris ne abu-isaam se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) peeney ki cheez mein teen martaba saans letey they aur farmatey they : ye (tareeqa) zyada sair karne waalaa, zyada mehfooz aur zyada mazedaar hai. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main (bhi) peeney ki cheez mein teen martaba saans leta hun."
5288,"Hisham dustwaai ne abu isaam se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki aur kaha : bartan mein (se peetey huey)."
5289,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein doodh pesh kiya gaya jis mein (thanda karne ke liye) pani milaya gaya tha. aap ki daain taraf aik dehati betha hua tha aur baain taraf Hazrat Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne doodh piyaa , phir dehati ko diya aur farmaya : dayan , uske baad phir dayan (muqaddam hoga)."
5290,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina mein tashrif laey to main das baras ka tha aur jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui to main bees saal ka tha. meri maain ( walida , khaalaaein , phoophiyaan ( musalsal mujhey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat karne ka shauq dilaya karti thin. aik martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey ghar tashrif laaey, ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye paaltu bakri ka doodh dohaa aur is mein ghar ke kuwey ka pani milaya gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey nosh farmaya to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz ki. aur us waqt Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baain taraf they. Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! Abu-Bakar ko inayat farma dijiye, lekin aap ne wo ( doodh ka bartan ( apni daain taraf ( baithey huey) baddoo ko thamaa diya aur farmaya : dayan , phir (uske baad wala) dayan."
5291,"abu tawaala Abdullah-bin-Abdur-Rehman Ansari se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko hadis bayan kartey huey suna, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey ghar mein aaey aur pani maanga . ham ne bakri ka doodh dohaa , phir usmein apne us kunein se pani milaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko diya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne piyaa aur saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baain taraf baithey they aur saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) samney aur daain taraf aik dehati tha. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sair ho kar pi liya to saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) ki taraf ishara kartey huey kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! ye Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hain. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (baqi) dehati ko diya aur saiyedna Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko nahi diya aur farmaya ke daain taraf waley muqaddam hain daain taraf waale, phir daain taraf waley . saiyedna Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye sunnat hai, ye sunnat hai, ye sunnat hai."
5292,"imam Malik-bin-Anas ne abu-Hazim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Sahal-bin-Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas peeney ki koi cheez aai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se piyaa . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daain taraf aik ladka tha aur baain taraf badey log they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ladkey se farmaya ke to mujh ko badey logon ko pahley dene ki ijazat deta hai? wo bola ke nahi Allah ki qism mein apna hissey kisi doosrey ko nahi dena chahta . ye sun kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us ladkey ke hath mein de diya."
5293,"Abdul-Azeez-bin-abi-Hazim aur Yaqoob-bin-Abdur-Rehman al-qaari , donon ne abu-Hazim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki, un donon ne ye nahi kaha : aap ne wo ( piyala uske hath par) rakh diya, albatta Yaqoob ki riwayat mein is tarah hai. ke aap ne wo (piyala) usey ata farma diya."
5294,"Amr ne ata' se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs khana khaaey to us waqt tak apna hath saaf na karey jab tak usey (apni ungliyon ko) khud na chaat ley ya kisi aur ko na chatwaaley. (jisey mohabbat ho wo chaat sakta hai.)"
5295,"ibne-Juraij ne hamein hadis sunai, kaha : maine Ata se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs khana khaaey to wo us waqt tak apna hath saaf na karey, jab tak usey khud na chaat ley ya kisi aur ko na chatwaaley."
5296,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Zuhair-bin-Harab aur Muhammad-bin-Hatim ne kaha : hamein ibne-Mehdi ne Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Sad-bin-Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : maine dekha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khaney ke baad apni teen ungliyan chaat rahe they. ibne- Hatim ne teen ka zikr nahi kiya. aur ibne-Abi-Sheba ki riwayat mein) ibne- Kab-bin-Malik ke bajaey) Abdur-Rehman-bin-Kab se riwayat hai, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, ke alfaz hain."
5297,"abu-Muawiya ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Sad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) teen ungliyon se khaatey they aur saaf karne se pahley apna hath (teen ungliyan) chaat-letey they."
5298,Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Hisham ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Sad se hadis bayan ki ke Abdur-Rehman-bin-Kab. ya Abdullah-bin-Kab. ne apne walid Kab (bin-Malik ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne unko hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) teen ungliyon se khaatey they aur jab khaney se farigh hotey to in ko chaat letey they.
5299,"(Abdullah) ibne-Numair ne kaha : hamein Hisham ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Sad se hadis bayan ki ke Abdur-Rehman-bin-Kab-bin-Malik aur Abdullah-bin-Kab donon ne. padhi. ya unmein se aik ne. padhi. apne walid Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
5300,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ungliyan aur piyala chaatney ka hukm diya aur farmaya : tum nahi jantey iske kis hissey mein barkat hai."
5301,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ( Sory ( ne abu-Zubair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se kisi shakhs ka luqma gir jaey to wo usey utha ley aur is par jo na-pasandida cheez (tinka, mitti) lagi hai usko achi tarah saaf kar ley aur usey kha ley , us luqmey ko shaitan ke liye na chhodey, aur jab tak apni ungliyon ko chaat na ley. us waqt tak apne hath ko roomaal se saaf na karey, kyonke usey malum nahi ke iske khaney ke kis hissey mein barkat hai."
5302,Abu-Dawud hafri aur Abdur-Razzaq donon ne Sufiyan ( Sory ( se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki. un donon ki hadis mein hai : aur apna hath roomaal se na poonchhey yahan tak ke usey chaat ley ya chatwaaley aur uske baad waley alfaz bhi hain.
5303,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : shaitan tum mein se har aik ki har haalat mein uske paas hazir hota hai yahan tak ke khaney ke waqt bhi, jab tum mein se kisi se luqma gir jaey to jo kuchh usey lag gaya hai. usey saaf karke kha ley aur usey shaitan ke liye na chhodey aur jab ( khaney se) farigh ho to apni ungliyan chaat ley kyonke usey pata nahi ke iske khaney ke kis hissey mein barkat hai."
5304,abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki : jab tum mein se kisi ka luqma gir jaey aakhir tak aur hadis ka shuruati hissey : shaitan tumharey paas hazir hota hai zikr nahi kya.
5305,"Muhammad-bin-Fuzail ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh aur Abu-Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( ungliyan ( chaatney ke barey mein riwayat bayan ki aur abu Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aur luqmey ka zikr kya, un donon (Jareer aur abu-Muawia) ki hadis ki tarah."
5306,"Behaz ne kaha : hamein Hammaad-bin-Salma ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jis waqt khana khaatey to ( aakhir mein) apni teen ungliyon ko chaat-tey aur kaha : aap ne farmaya : jab tum mein se kisi ka luqma gir jaey to wo us se na-pasandida cheez ko door kar ley aur kha ley aur usko shaitan ke liye na chhodey aur aap ne hamein piyala saaf karne ka hukm diya aur farmaya : tum nahi jantey ke tumharey khaney ke kis hissey mein barkat hai."
5307,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs khana khaaey to apni ungliyon ko chaat ley, kyonke wo nahi janta ke unmein se kis mein barkat hai."
5308,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne kaha : hamein Hammad ne isi sanad ke sath hadis sunai, magar unhon-ne kaha : tum mein se har aik piyala saaf kare. aur farmaya : tumharey kis khaney (ke kis hissey) mein barkat hai, ya ( farmaya : ( kis khaney main tumharey liye barkat dali jati hai."
5309,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu-Waail se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ke Ansar mein aik aadmi jiska naam abu-Shuaib (Raziallahu anhu) tha, jiska aik ghulam tha jo gosht bechaa karta tha. us Ansari ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehrey par bhook malum hui to apne ghulam se kaha ke ham panch aadmiyon ke liye khana taiyaar kar kyonke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dawat karna chahta hun. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) panch aadmiyon mein paanchwein hongey. rawi kehta hai ke usne khana taiyaar kiya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aa kar dawat di aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) panch mein paanchwein they. unke sath aik aadmi ho gaya to jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) darwazey par pahunchey to (sahibe khaana se) farmaya ke ye shakhs hamarey sath chala aaya hai, agar to chahey to isko ijazat de, warna ye lot jaeyga usne kaha ke nahi ya Rasulullah ! balke mein usko ijazat deta hun."
5310,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne hamein yahi hadis abu-Muawiya se bayan ki, isi ke saath ye hadis hamein Nasar-bin-Ali jahazmi aur abu-Saeed ashajj ne bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein abu-Usama ne hadis bayan ki, Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz ne kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, isi ke saath hamein Abdullah-bin-Abdur-Rehman daarmi ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Yousuf ne Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, un sab ( abu-Muawiya , Shoba aur Sufiyan ( ne Aamash se riwayat ki, unhon-ne abu-Waail se, unhon-ne abu Masood se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis isi tarah bayan ki jis tarah Jarir ki hadis hai. Nasar-bin-Ali ne us hadis ki apni riwayat mein kaha : hamein abu-Usama ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Aamash se Shaqeeq-bin-Salma se, unhon-ne abu Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se, phir poori hadis bayan ki."
5311,"Ammar-bin-razeeq ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu-Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, isi ke saath Zuhair ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne Shaqiq se, unhon-ne abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, isi ke saath (Zuhair ne) Aamash se, unhon-ne Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se yahi hadis bayan ki."
5312,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka aik Faaris se talluq rakhney wala padosi shorba achchha banata tha, us ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye shorba taiyaar kya, phir aakar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dawat di. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf ishara karke farmaya : unko bhi dawat hai? usne kaha : nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi (mujhey bhi tumhari dawat qabool nahi ( wo dobara Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bulaney aaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : unko bhi ? usne kaha : nahi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : to nahi. wo phir dawat dene ke liye aaya, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : unko bhi ? to teesri baar usne kaha : haan. phir aap donon aik doosrey ke peechhey chal padey yahan tak ke uske ghar aa gaey."
5313,"Khalaf bin khaleefa ne Yazeed bin kaisaan se, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik baar raat ya din ko bahar nikley aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saiyedna Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha to puchha ke tumhen is waqt kon si cheez ghar se nikal laai hai? unhon-ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! bhook ke maarey . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qism uski jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, main bhi usi wjah se nikla hun, chalo. phir wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath chaley, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik Ansari ke darwazey par aaey, wo apne ghar mein nahi tha. uski aurat ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha to usne khush aamadeed kaha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke falan shakhs (uske khawind ke mutaalliq farmaya ( kahan gaya hai? wo boli ke hamarey liye meetha pani leney gaya hai (is hadis se malum hua ke uzr se ajnabi aurat se baat karna aur usko jawab dena durust hai, isi tarah aurat us mard ko ghar bula sakti hai jiske aaney se khawind razi ho ( itney mein wo Ansari mard aa gaya to usne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke donon sathiyon ko dekha to kaha ke Allah Taala ka shukr hai ke aaj ke din kisi ke paas aisey mehman nahi hain jaisey mere paas hain. phir gaya aur khajoor ka aik khosha lekar aaya jis mein gadar, sukhi aur taaza khajoorein thin aur kehney laga ke usmein se khaaiye phir us ne chhuri li to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke doodh wali bakri mat kaatna. us ne aik bakri kaati aur sab ne uska gosht khaya aur khajoor bhi khaai aur pani piya. jab khaney peeney se sair huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saiyedna Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke qism uski jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, qiyamat ke din tum se us nemat ke barey mein sawal hoga ke tum apne gharon se bhook ke maarey nikley aur nahi lautey yahan tak ke tumhen ye nemat mili . (is Fazal par sawal zaroor hoga.)"
5314,"Abdul-Wahid bin Ziyad ne kaha : hamein Yazeed ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abu-Hazim ne hadis sunai, kaha : maine Hazrat abu Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : aik roz Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) baithey huey they, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) unke sath they. itney main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas tashrif ley aaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum donon ko kis cheez ne yahan bitha rakha hai? donon ne kaha : qism us zaat ki jisne aapko haq ke sath bheja hai ! hamein bhook ne apne gharon se nikala hai. phir Khalaf bin khaleefa ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
5315,"Hajjaj-bin shaair ne kaha : Suhak bin Mukhlid ne mujhey aik ruqey se hadis bayan ki, usey mere samney rakha phir usey padha, kaha : mujhey Hanzala bin Usman ne iske barey mein bataya, kaha : hamein Saeed bin Mina ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : ke jab (Madina ke gird) khandaq khodi gaee to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bhooka paya. main apni biwi ke paas lota aur kaha ke terey paas kuchh hai? kyonke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bahut bhooka paya hai. us ne aik thailaa nikala jis mein aik saa jo they aur hamarey paas bakri ka pala hua bachcha tha, maine usko zabah kya aur meri aurat ne aata peesa. wo bhi mere sath hi farigh hui maine uska gosht kaat kar handi mein dala. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas palatney laga to aurat boli ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathiyon ke samney ruswa na karna (kyonke khana thoda hai kahin bahut se aadmiyon ki dawat na kar dena ( . main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur chupkey se arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! maine aik bakri ka bachcha zabah kya hai aur aik saa jo ka aata jo hamarey paas tha, taiyaar kya hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chand logon ko apne sath lekar tashrif laaiye. ye sun kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pukara aur farmaya ke aey khandaq waalo! Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne tumhari dawat ki hai to chalo aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apni handi ko mat utaarna aur aatey ki roti mat pakaana, jab tak mein na aa jaun. phir main ghar mein aaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi tashrif laey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aagey-aagey they aur log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey they. main apni aurat ke paas aaya, wo boli ke tu hi pareshan hoga aur log tujhey hi bura kahengey. maine kaha ke maine to wahi kya jo to ne kaha tha ( lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne elaan kar diya aur sab ko dawat suna di ( maine wo aata nikala to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna luaab Mubarak usmein daala aur barkat ki dua ki, phir hamari handi ki taraf chaley aur is mein bhi luaab Mubarak daala aur barkat ki dua ki. iske baad (meri aurat se) farmaya ke aik roti pakaaney wali aur bula ley jo terey sath mil kar pakaaey aur handi mein se doi nikal kar nikaalti ja, usko utaarna mat. saiyedna Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik hazaar aadmi they, isliye main qism khata hun ke sab ne khaya, yahan tak ke chhod diya aur lot gaey aur handi ka wahi haal tha, ubal rahi thi aur aata bhi waisa hi tha, uski rotiyaan bin rahi thin."
5316,"Ishaq bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha ne kaha ke unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki awaz suni hai kamzor thi. mujhey mehsus hota hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bhook lagi hai. kya tumharey paas koi cheez hai? unhon-ne kaha : haan, phir unhon-ne jo ki kuchh rotiyan nikaalin, phir apni odhni li iske aik hissey mein rotiyan lapetein, phir unko mere kapdon ke nichey chipa ya aur us (odhni) ka Baqiya hissey chadar ki tarah mere uper daal diya, phir mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhej diya. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main un rotiyon ko lekar gaya, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko masjid mein baithey paya aur aap ke sath doosrey log maujood they, main unke paas khada ho gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumhen abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne bheja hai? maine kaha : ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya khaney ke liye? maine kaha : ji haan. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sathiyon se kaha chalo Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha huzoor (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rawana huey aur main unke aagey-aagey chal pada, yahan tak ke main Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur unko bataya. Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : Umme-Sulaim ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( baqi ( logon samet aagey hain, aur hamarey paas itna ( khana ( nahi hai ke unko khila sakein. unhon-ne kaha : Allah aur uska rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zyada jaanney waley hain. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) aagey badhey aur) ja kar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se miley. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke sath aaey aur wo donon ghar mein dakhil ho gaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Umme-Sulaim ! jo kuchh tumharey paas hai wo ley aao . wo yahi rotiyaan ley aaein, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke barey mein hukm diya, un ( rotiyon (ke chhotey chhotey tukdey kar diye gaey. Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna ghi ka kuppa (chamdey ka gol bartan) un ( rotiyon ( par nichod kar saalan shamil kar diya, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein jo kuchh Allah ne chaha padha, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : das aadmiyon ko aaney ki ijazat do. unhon (abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu)) ne das aadmiyon ko ijazat di, unhon-ne khana khaya yahan tak ke sair ho gaey aur bahar chaley gaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya : das aadmiyon ko ijazat do. unhon-ne ijazat di, un sab ne khaya sair ho gaey aur bahar chaley gaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya : das aadmiyon ko ijazat do yahan tak ke sab logon ne kha liya aur sair ho gaey. wo 70 ya assi log they."
5317,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Sad bin Saeed ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bulaney ke liye aap ke paas bheja , unhon-ne khana taiyaar kya tha. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main aaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ke sath baithey huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne meri taraf dekha to mujhey sharm aai , maine kaha : Hazrat abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ki dawat qabool farmaiye . is par aap ne logon se kaha : utho . Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! maine to aap ke liye (khaney ki) kuchh thodi si cheez taiyaar ki hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us khaney ko chhuwa aur is mein barkat ki dua ki, phir farmaya : mere sathiyon mein se das ko andar lao aur) unse) farmaya : khaao aur aap ne unke liye apni ungliyon ke darmyan se kuchh nikala tha ( barkat shamil ki thi) , so unhon-ne khaya , sair ho gaey, aur bahar chaley gaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : das aadmiyon ko andar laao. phir unhon-ne khaya, sair ho gaey aur chaley gaey, wo das das ko andar latey aur das das ko bahar bhejtey rahe, yahan tak ke unmein se koi baqi na bacha magar sab ne kha liya aur sair ho gaey, phir usko sameta to wo itna hi tha jitna unke khaney (ke shuruat (ke waqt tha."
5318,"Yahya-bin-Saeed umwi ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis sunai kaha : hamein Sad bin Saeed ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja phir ibne-Numair ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne uske aakhir mein yun kaha : jo bacha tha aap ne usey lekar ikattha kya phir usmein barkat ki dua ki, kaha : to wo (phir se) utna hi ho gaya, jitna tha phir farmaya : ye tumharey liye hai. (aap ne khaney ke shuru mein bhi barkat ki dua ki aur aakhir mein bhii. ("
5319,"Abdur-Rehman bin abi Lela ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke wo khas taur par sirf Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye khana taiyaar kar de phir mujhey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf bheja gaya iske baad hadis bayan ki aur is mein ye ( bhi) kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( khaney par) apna hath rakha aur is par bismillaah padhi phir farmaya : das aadmiyon ko andar aaney ki) ijazat do unhon-ne das aadmiyon ko ijazat di wo andar aaey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya bismillaah padho aur khaao to un logon ne khaya, yahan tak ke assi aadmiyon ke sath aisa hi kya (das das ko andar bulaya bismillaah padh kar khaney ko kaha) iske baad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur ghar walon ne khaya aur (phir bhi) unhon-ne khana bacha diya."
5320,"Yahya (maazni) ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke khaney ka yahi qissa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale se bayan kya aur is mein kaha : Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) darwazey par khadey ho gaey. yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey, Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Allah ke rasool! sirf thoda sa khana tha aap ne farmaya : ley aao Allah Taala an-qareeb usmein barkat daal dega."
5321,"Abdullah bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis riwayat ki aur is mein kaha : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tanawul farmaya aur ghar walon ne khaya aur itna bacha diya jo unhon-ne padausiyon ko) bhi) bhijwa diya."
5322,"Amr bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko masjid mein letey huey dekha aap peeth aur pet ke bal karwatein ley rahe they. phir wo Hazrat Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko masjid mein letey huey dekha hai aap peeth se pet ke bal karwatein ley rahe they aur mera khayal hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhookey hain aur) saari ( hadis bayan ki aur is mein ye kaha : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hazrat abu Talha , Hazrat Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) aur Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne khana khaya aur kuchh khana bach gaya jo ham ne apne padausiyon ko hadiya kar diya."
5323,Usama ne bataya ke Yaqoob bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha ne unhein hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna keh rahe they. aik din mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir hua maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko masjid main apne sathiyon ke sath baithey huey unse baatein kartey huey paya. aap ne pet par aik patthar ko aik chodi si patti se baandh rakha tha. padhi. Usama ne kaha : mujhey shak hai (ke Yaqoob ne patthar ka lafz bola ya nahi ( . maine aap ke aik sathi se puchha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne batan ko kyon baandh rakha hai? logon ne bataya : bhook ki bina par. phir main abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya wo ( meri walida (Hazrat Umme-Sulaim binte-Milhaan (Raziallahu anhu) ke khawind they maine unse kaha : abba jaan! maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha hai ke aap ne pet par patti baandh rakhi hai maine aap ke kuchh sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) se puchha : iski kya waja hai? unhon-ne kaha bhook. phir Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) meri maa ke paas gaey aur puchha : ke koi cheez hai? unhon-ne kaha : haan mere paas roti ke tukdey aur kuchh khajoorein hain agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) akeley hamarey paas tashrif ley aaein to ham aapko sair karke khila dengey aur agar koi aur bhi aap ke sath aaya to ye khana kam hoga phir baqi saari hadis bayan ki.
5324,"Nazar bin Anas ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale se Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke khaney ke barey mein un sab ki hadis ke mutabiq riwayat kya."
5325,"Ishaq bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna keh rahe they : aik darzi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apne taiyaar kiye huey khaney ki dawat di, Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath us khaney par gaya, us ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney jo ki roti aur shorba rakha, usmein kadu aur chhotey tukdon ki sura mein mehfooz kya hua gosht tha Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) piyaley ki charon taraf se kadu talash kar rahe they. (hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : main isi din se kadu ko pasand karta hun."
5326,"Sulaiman-bin Mughira ne Sabit se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khaney ki dawat di mein bhi aap ke sath gaya. aap ke liye shorba laya gaya usmein kadu ( bhi) tha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usmein se kadu khaney lagey wo aapko achchha lag raha tha. jab maine ye baat dekhi to main kadu (ke tukdey (aap ke samney karne laga aur khud na khaaey . Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha is din ke baad se mujhey kadu bahut achchha lagta hai."
5327,"Mamar ne Sabit Bunani aur Aasim ahwal se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs ne jo darzi tha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dawat di aur ye izafa kya ke Sabit ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : iske baad jab bhi mere liye khana banta hai aur main aisa kar sakta hun ke usmein kadu daala jaey to daala jata hai."
5328,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Yazeed bin Khumair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin Basar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere walid ke yahan mehman huey ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein khajoor paneer aur ghi se taiyaar kya hua halwa pesh kya, aap ne usmein se khaya, phir aap ke samney khajoorein pesh ki gain to aap khajoorein kha rahe they. aur guthliyan apni 2 ungliyon ke darmyan daltey ja rahe they. ( khaney ke liye) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne shahadat ki aur darmyani ungli ikatthi ki hui thin. Shoba ne kaha : mera guman ( ghalib ( hai aur insha-Allah ye baat yani guthliyon ko 2 ungliyon ke darmyan daalna us ( hadis) mein hai. phir (aap ke samney ( mashroob laya gaya. aap ne usey piya, phir apni daain taraf waley ko de diya. ( Abdullah-bin Basar (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to mere walid ne jab unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari ki lagaam pakdi hui thi kaha : hamarey liye Allah se dua farmaiye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( dua kartey huey) farmaya : aey Allah! tu ney unhein jo rizq diya hai is mein unke liye barkat daal de aur unke gunah bakhsh de aur un par raham farma."
5329,ibne-abi Adi aur Yahya bin Hammad donon ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki. guthliyon ko 2 ungliyon ke darmyan dalney ke barey mein shak (ka izhar) nahi kya.
5330,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko taaza khajoor ke sath kakdi khaatey huey dekha."
5331,"Hafs bin Ghiyas ne Musab bin Sulaim se riwayat ki, kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) donon ghutney khadey karke thodey se zamin par lag kar baithey they. khajoorein kha rahe they."
5332,"Zuhair-bin-Harab aur ibne-abi-Umar ne Sufiyan-bin-Uena se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Musab bin Sulaim se unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki : kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein khajoorein pesh ki gain . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is tarah baithey huey unko taqseem farmane lagey jaisey aap abhi uthney lagey hon (baithney ki wahi kaifiyat jo pichhli hadis mein bayan hui doosrey lafzon mein batai gaee hai) aur aap usmein se jaldi-jaldi chand daney kha rahe they. Zuhair ki. riwayat mein) ذَريعاً (ke bajaey ( حَثِيثًا (ka lafz hai yani baghair kisi ehtimaam ke jaldi-jaldi."
5333,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine jabla bin Suhem se suna ke Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) hamein khajooron ka raashan detey they un dinon log qahat-sali ka shikar they. aur ham ( khajoorein ( khaatey they. ham kha rahe hotey to Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey qareeb se guzartey aur farmatey : ikatthi 2-2 khajoorein mat khaao Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ikatthi 2-2 khajoorein khaney se mana farmaya hai, siwaey iske ke aadmi apne ( sath khaney waale) bhai se ijazat ley. Shoba ne kaha : mera yahi khayal hai ke ye jumla yani ijazat lena Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ka apna qaul hai. ( unhon-ne usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat nahi kya. ("
5334,"Ubaidullah ke walid Muaz aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi donon ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki. un donon ki riwayat mein Shoba ka aur un ( jabla bin Suhem (ka ye qaul maujood nahi, un dinon log qahat-sali (suka) ka shikar they."
5335,"Sufiyan ne jabla bin Suhem se riwayat ki kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is se mana farmaya hai ke koi shakhs sathiyon se ijazat liye baghair ikatthi 2-2 khajoorein khaaey."
5336,Urwa ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aisey ghar ke log bhookey nahi rahtey jinke paas khajoorein hon.
5337,"abu-Rijaal Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman ne apni walida (Umra binte-Abdur-Rehman ansariya) se unhon-ne Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Aaisha! jis ghar mein khajoorein na hon usmein rehney waley bhookey hain Aaisha! jis ghar mein khajoorein na hon usmein rehney waley bhookey hain. jis ghar mein khajoorein na hon usmein rehney waley bhookey hain. ya ( farmaya (us ghar ke log bhookey reh jatey hain. aap ne ye kalimaat 2 ya teen baar farmaai ."
5338,"Abdullah-bin Abdur-Rehman ne Aamir bin Sad-bin-abi-Waqas se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne subah ke waqt Madina ke 2 pathreeley maidaanon ke darmyan ki saat (7) khajoorein kha lin, usko Sham (Syria) tak koi zahar nuqsan nahi pahunchaeyga."
5339,"abu-Usama ne Hashim bin Hashim se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Aamir bin Sad-bin-abi-Waqas se suna, keh rahe they maine (apne walid (Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna, jisne subah ko saat (7) ajwa khajoorein kha lin us din usey zahar nuqsan pahuncha sakega na jadu."
5340,"Marwan bin Muawiya farazi aur abu badr shujaa bin Waleed donon ne Hashim bin Hashim se, isi sanad ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki. wo donon ye nahi kehtey : maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna."
5341,Abdullah-bin-abi-ateeq ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (Madina ke) oopri hissey ki ajwa khajooron mein shifa hai ya ( farmaya : ( subah ke awwal waqt mein unka istemal tiryaq hai.
5342,"Jarir aur Umar-bin-Ubaid ne abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se unhon-ne Amr-bin-Hurais se, unhon-ne Saeed bin Zaid-bin-Amr-bin-Nufail se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna khumbi 'man' (wo khana jo salwaa ke sath Bani-Israeel ke liye aasman ki taraf se utra tha) ki aik qism hai aur iska pani aankhon ke liye shifa hai."
5343,"Shoba ne abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Amr-bin-Hurais se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kaha : maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna ke farma rahe they khumbi 'man' ki aik qism hai aur uska pani aankhon ke liye shifa hai."
5344,"Shoba ne kaha : mujhey Hakam-bin-Utaiba ne Hasan arni se khabar di unhon-ne Amr-bin-Hurais se, unhon-ne Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. Shoba ne kaha : jab mujh se Hakam ne ye riwayat ki to maine Abdul-Malik ki riwayat ki wjah se usko munkar qarar na diya."
5345,"Absar ne Mutarrif se, unhon-ne Hasan se, unhon-ne Amr-bin-Hurais se unhon-ne Saeed bin Zaid-bin-Amr-bin-Nufail (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : khumbii us 'man' mein se hai jisey Allah Taala ne Bani-Israeel ke liye nazil kya tha aur uska pani aankhon ke liye shifa hai."
5346,"Jarir ne Mutarrif se unhon-ne Hakam-bin-Utaiba se unhon-ne Hasan arni se unhon-ne Amr-bin-Hurais se, unhon-ne Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, ke aap ne farmaya : khumbi us 'man' mein se hai jisey Allah Taala ne Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) ko) aasman se) utaar kar ata kya tha aur uska pani aankhon ke liye shifa hai."
5347,"Sufiyan ne abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Amr-bin-Hurais se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se suna tha keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : khumbi us man mein se hai jisey izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne Bani-Israeel par) aasman se) utara tha aur iska pani aankhon ke liye shifa hai."
5348,"Shahar bin Hoshab ne kaha : maine abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se suna, unhon-ne kaha : main Abdul-Malik se mila to unhon-ne mujhey Amr-bin-Hurais se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : khumbi man mein se hai aur iska pani aankhon ke liye shifa hai."
5349,"abu-Salma Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham marruz-zohran (ke maqam ( par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they aur ham peelu chun rahe they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : unmein se siyah peelu chuno. ham ne arz ki, Allah ke rasool! yun lagta hai jaisey aap ne bakriyan charai hon Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan koi Nabi nahi jisne bakriyan na charai hon. ya isi tarah ki baat irshad farmai ."
5350,"Yahya bin Hassan ne kaha ke hamein Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : saalanon mein se umda ya (farmaya) umda saalan sirka hai."
5351,Yahya bin Saleh Wuhazi ne kaha ke hamein Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne isi sanad ke sath hadis sunai aur kaha : saalanon mein se umda aur shak nahi kya.
5352,abu Bishr ne abu Sufiyan (Talha bin Naafe ( se unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne ghar walon se saalan ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne kaha : hamarey paas to sirf sirka hai aap ne sirka mangaya aur usi ke sath roti khana shuru kar di. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they. sirka umda saalan hai sirka umda saalan hai.
5353,"Ismail bin-Ulaih ne Musanna bin Saeed se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Talha bin Naafe ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they. aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mera hath pakad kar apne ghar le gaey to khaadim aap ke liye roti ke kuchh tukdey nikal kar laya aap ne puchha : koi saalan nahi hai? usne kaha : thoda sa sirka hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah sirka umda saalan hai. Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jab se maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye suna hai main sirka pasand karta hun aur Talha ( rawi ( ne kaha : jab se maine Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadis suni hai main bhi sar ke ko pasand karta hun."
5354,"Nasar ke walid Ali jahazmi ne kaha : hamein Musanna bin Saeed ne Talha bin Naafe se hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unka hath pakad kar apne ghar le gaey unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qaul : sirka umda saalan hai tak ibne-Ulaih ki hadis ki tarah bayan ki aur baad ka hissa bayan nahi kya."
5355,"Hajjaj-bin abi Zenab ne kaha : mujhey abu Sufiyan Talha bin Naafe ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kaha : main kisi ghar mein betha hua tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka guzar mere paas se hua, aap ne meri taraf ishara kya main uth kar aap ke paas aaya aap ne mera hath pakda aur chal padey yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) paak beeviyon (Raziallahu anhu) ke hujron mein se kisi ke hujrey par aaey aur andar dakhil ho gaey phir mujhey bhi aaney ki ijazat di, main (hujra anwar mein) unke hijaab ke aalim mein dakhil hua aap ne farmaya : kuchh khaney ko hai? ghar walon ne kaha : hai aur teen rotiyan laai gain aur unko aik ooni rumaal (dasterkhan) par rakh diya gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik roti apne samney rakhi aur aik roti mere samney rakhi phir aap ne teesri ke 2 tukdey kiye, aadhi apne samney rakhi aur aadhi mere samney rakhi phir aap ne puchha : koi saalan bhi hai? ghar walon ne kaha : thoda sa sirka hai iske siwa aur kuchh nahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ley aao sirka kya khub saalan hai!"
5356,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Samak-bin-Harab se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Hazrat abu Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas koi khana laya jata to aap usmein se tanaawul farmatey aur jo bach jata usey mere paas bhej detey aik din aap ne mere paas bacha hua khana bheja jis mein se aap ne khud kuchh nahi khaya tha kyonke usmein (kachcha) lehsun tha maine aap se puchha : kya ye haram hai? aap ne farmaya : nahi lekin main uski badboo ki wjah se usey na-pasand karta hun. maine kaha : jo aapko na-pasand hai wo mujhey bhi na-pasand hai."
5357,Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki.
5358,"Hazrat Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam Aflah ne Hazrat Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke yahan mehman thehrey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nichey ke makan mein rahe aur saiyedna Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) uper ke darje mein they. aik baar saiyedna Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) raat ko jaagey aur kaha ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sar ke uper chala kartey hain, phir hat kar raat ko aik koney mein ho gaey. phir uske baad saiyedna abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se uper janey ke liye kaha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nichey ka makan aaraam ka hai) rehney walon ke liye aur aaney walon ke liye aur usi liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nichey ke makan mein rahtey they). saiyedna Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, main us chhat par nahi reh sakta jiske nichey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hun. ye sun kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uper ke darja mein tashrif le gaey aur Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) nichey ke darjey mein aa gaey. saiyedna abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye khana taiyaar kartey they, phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se khana aata (aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usmein se khaatey aur uske baad bacha hua khana wapas jata ( to saiyedna abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu)) aadmi se) poochhtey ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ungliyan khaney ki kis jagah par lagi hain aur wo wahin se ( barkat ke liye) khaatey . aik din saiyedna abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) ne khana pakaaya, jis mein lehsun tha. jab khana wapas gaya to saiyedna abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ungliyan kahan lagi thin ? unhein bataya gaya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khana nahi khaaya. ye sun kar saiyedna abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) ghabra gaey aur uper gaey aur puchha ke kya lehsun haram hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi, lekin main usey na-pasand karta hun. saiyedna abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha jo cheez Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko na-pasand hai, mujhey bhi na-pasand hai. saiyedna abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ( Farishtey ( aatey they (aur farishton ko lehsun ki bo se takleef hoti isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) na khaatey ( ."
5359,"Jarir bin abdul-Hameed ne Fuzel bin Ghazawaan se, unhon-ne abu-Hazim Ashjai se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ke aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha ke mujhey (khaney peeney ki) badi takleef hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni kisi paak bevi ke paas kehla bheja, wo bolin ke qism uski jisne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko sachchai ke sath bheja hai ke mere paas to pani ke siwa kuchh nahi hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dusri bevi ke paas bheja to unhon-ne bhi aisa hi kaha, yahan tak ke sab paak beeviyan (Raziallahu anhu) anhunna se yahi jawab aaya ke hamarey paas pani ke siwa kuchh nahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aaj ki raat kon uski mehmani karta hai? Allah Taala is par rehem karey, tab aik Ansari utha aur kehney laga ke ya Rasulullah! main karta hun. phir wo usko apne thikaaney par ley gaya aur apni biwi se kaha ke terey paas kuchh hai? wo boli ke kuchh nahi albatta mere bachchon ka khana hai. Ansari ne kaha ke bachchon se kuchh bahana kar de aur jab hamara mehman andar aaey aur dekhna jab ham khaney lagein to charagh bujha dena. to jab wo khaney laga to wo uthi aur charagh bujhaa diya (rawi) kehta hai wo baithey aur mehman khata raha. us ne aisa hi kya aur miyan-biwi bhookey baithey rahe aur mehman ne khana khaaya. jab subah hui to wo Ansari Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne us se tajjub kya jo tum ne raat ko apne mehman ke sath kya (yani khush hua) ."
5360,"Wakee ne Fuzel bin Ghazawaan se, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Ansar mein se aik aadmi ke paas aik mehman ne raat guzari, unke paas sirf apna aur bachchon ka khana tha, us ne apni biwi se kaha, bachchon ko sula 2 aur charagh bhuja do aur jo khana tumharey paas hai wo mehman ke qareeb kar do, tab ye aayat nazil hui : ( وَيُؤْثِرُونَ عَلَىٰ أَنفُسِهِمْ وَلَوْ كَانَ بِهِمْ خَصَاصَةٌ ( wo ( dusron ko) khud par tarjeeh detey hain chahey unhein sakht zarurat laahiq ho."
5361,"ibne- Fuzel ne apne walid se, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya taake Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey mehman bana len , aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas uski mezbaani ke liye kuchh bhi na tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi aisa shakhs hai jo usko mehman banaey ? Allah Taala is par raham farmaai ! Ansar mein se aik shakhs khadey ho gaey, unhein abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) kaha jata tha, wo us ( mehman ( ko apne ghar le gaey, iske baad Jarir ki hadis ke mutabiq hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne bhi Wakee ki tarah aayat nazil honey ka zikr kya."
5362,"Shababa bin sawar ne kaha : hamein Sulaiman-bin Mughira ne Sabit se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi Lela se, unhon-ne Hazrat Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, saiyedna Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main aur mere donon sathi aaey aur) faaqa wghaira ki) takleef se hamari aankhon aur kanon ki quwwat jati rahi thi. ham apne aapko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab par pesh kartey they lekin koi hamein qabool na karta tha. aakhir ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein apne ghar ley gaey. wahan teen bakriyan thin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unka doodh doho, ham tum sab piengey phir ham unka doodh doha kartey aur ham mein se har aik apna hissey pi leta aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hissa rakh chhodtey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko tashrif latey aur aisi awaz se salam kartey jis se soney wala na jaagey aur jaagney wala sun ley. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein aatey , Namaz padhtey , phir apne doodh ke paas aatey aur usko peetey. aik raat jab main apna hissey pi chuka tha ke shaitan ne mujhey bhadkaaya. shaitan ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to Ansar ke paas jatey hain, wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko tohfey detey hain aur jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko zarurat hai, mil jata hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us aik ghoont doodh ki kya zarurat hogi? aakhir mein aaya aur wo doodh pi gaya. jab doodh pet mein sama gaya aur mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke ab wo doodh nahi milney ka to us waqt shaitan ne mujhey nadaamat ki aur kehney laga ke teri kharabi ho tu ney kya kaam kiya? tu ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hissa pi liya, ab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aaeingey aur doodh ko na paeingey to tujh par baddua karengey aur teri duniya aur aakhirat donon tabah hongi. main aik chadar odhey huey tha jab usko paon par daalta to sar khul jata aur jab sar dhaanpta to paon khul jatey they aur mujhey neend bhi na aa rahi thi jabke mere sathi so gaey aur unhon-ne ye kaam nahi kya tha jo maine kya tha. aakhir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aaey aur mamool (routine) ke muwafiq salam kya, phir masjid mein aaey aur Namaz padhi, iske baad doodh ke paas aaey, bartan khola to usmein kuchh na tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna sar aasman ki taraf uthaya main samjha ke ab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baddua kartey hain aur main tabah hua. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Allah ! khila usko jo mujhey khilaey aur pila usko jo mujhey pilaaey . ye sun kar maine apni chadar ko mazbut baandha, chhuri li aur bakriyon ki taraf chala ke jo unmein se motii ho usko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye zabah karun. dekha to uske than mein doodh bhara hua hai. phir dekha to aur bakriyon ke thanon mein bhi doodh bhara hua hai. maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar walon ka aik bartan liya jis mein wo doodh na dohtey they (yani usmein dohney ki khahish nahi kartey they). usmein maine doodh doha, yahan tak ke uper jhaag aa gaya ( itna bahut doodh nikla (aur main usko lekar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum ne apne hissey ka doodh raat ko piyaa ya nahi ? maine arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! aap doodh peejiye . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pi kar mujhey diya to maine arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! aur peejiye . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aur piya. phir mujhey diya, jab mujhey malum ho gaya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sair ho gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dua maine ley li hai, tab main hansa , yahan tak ke khushi ke maarey zamin par gir gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Miqdad ! to ne koi buri baat ki? wo kya hai? maine arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! mera haal aisa hua aur maine aisa qasoor kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us waqt ka doodh (jo khilaf mamool (routine) utra ( Allah ki rehmat thi. tu ney mujh se pahley hi kyon na kaha ham apne donon sathiyon ko bhi jaga detey ke wo bhi ye doodh peetey ? maine arz kya ke qism uski jisne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko sachcha kalam de kar bheja hai ke ab mujhey koi parwah nahi jab aap ne Allah ki rehmat hasil kar li aur maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath hasil ki to koi bhi usko hasil kare."
5363,Nazar-bin-Shumail ne Sulaiman-bin Mughira se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki.
5364,"abu-Usmaan ne Hazrat Abdur-Rehman -bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : saiyedna Abdur-Rehman -bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik so tees (130) aadmi they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya kisi paas khana hai? aik shakhs ke paas aik saa anaaj nikla ya thoda kam ya zyada . phir wo sab goondha gaya. phir aik mushrik aaya, jiske baal bikhrey huey they lamba qad tha bakriyan lekar haankta hua Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas pahuncha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke to (bakri) bechtaa hai ya hadiya deta hai? usne kaha ke nahi bechta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se aik bakri kharidi to uska gosht taiyaar kya gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kaleji, gurdey. dil wghaira ko bhoonney ka hukm diya, (hazrat Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Allah ki qism ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik sau tees (130) aadmiyon mein se har aik shakhs ko uski kaleji wghaira ka aik tukda diya, jo shakhs maujood tha usko de diya aur jo maujood nahi tha uskey liye rakh liya. ( Abdur-Rehman -bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : aap ne (khaney ke liye) 2 badey pyaley banaey aur ham sab ne un 2 piyaalon mein se khaya aur sair ho gaey, donon piyaalon mein khana phir bhi bach gaya to maine usko oont par laad liya ya jis tarah unhon-ne kaha."
5365,"Motamir bin Sulaiman ke walid ne kaha : hamein abu-Usman ne hadis bayan ki ke unhein Hazrat Abdur-Rehman -bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke ashabe-Suffa mohtaaj log they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik baar farmaya ke jiske paas 2 aadmiyon ka khana ho wo teen ( teesrey : sahi Bukhari : 602 ( ko ley jaey. aur jiske paas char ka ho wo paanchwein ya chhatey ko bhi ley jaey aur saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) teen aadmiyon ko ley aaey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) das aadmiyon ko le gaey (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahal w ayaal bhi das ke qareeb they, to maano aadha khana mehmanon ke liye hua). saiyedna Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke hamarey ghar mein koi nahi tha siwaey mere bap aur meri maan ke. rawi ne kaha ke shayad apni biwi ka bhi kaha aur aik khaadim jo mere aur saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar mein tha. saiyedna Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne raat ka khana Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khaya, phir wahin thehrey rahe yahan tak ke isha ki Namaz padhi gaee. phir Namaz se farigh ho kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas lot gaey aur wahin rahe, yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey. gharaz badi raat guzarney ke baad jitni Allah Taala ko manzoor thi saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ghar aaey aur unki biwi ne kaha ke tum apne mehmaanon ko chhod kar kahan reh gaey they? saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tum ne unko khana nahi khilaaya? unhon-ne kaha ke mahmaanon ne tumharey aaney tak nahi khaya aur unhon-ne mehmaanon ke samney khana pesh kya tha lekin mehman un par na khaney mein ghalib huey. saiyedna Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main to (saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki naarazagi ke dar se) chhup gaya to unhon-ne mujhey pukara ke aey sust majhool ya ahmaq ! teri naak katey aur mujhey bura kaha aur mehmaanon se kaha ke khaao agarche ye khana khushgawar nahi hai (kyonke be waqt hai) aur saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main Allah ki qism mein usko kabhi bhi na khaaunga. saiyedna Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah ki qism ham jo luqma uthatey nichey wo khana utna hi badh jata, yahan tak ke ham sair ho gaey aur khana jitna pehley tha us se bhi zyada ho gaya. saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne us khaney ko dekha ke wo utna hi hai ya zyada ho gaya hai to unhon-ne apni aurat se kaha ke aey bani Faraas ki behan ye kya hai? wo boli ke meri aankhon ki thandak ki qism (yani Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki) ke ye to pahley se bhi zyada (ho gaya) hai teen hissey zyada hai. phir saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne usmein se khaya aur kaha ke maine jo qism khaai thi wo (ghussey mein) shaitan ki taraf se thi. phir aik luqma usmein se khaya, iske baad wo khana Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ley gaey. main bhi subah ko wahin tha aur hamarey aur aik qaum ke darmyan aqad tha (yani suleh ka iqrar tha) , to iqrar ki muddat guzar gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baara aadmi hamarey afsar kiye aur har aik ke sath log they aur Allah Taala janta hai ke har aik ke sath kitney log they. phir wo khana unke sath kar diya aur sab logon ne usmein se khaaya. ya jis tarah unhon-ne bayan kya."
5366,"Jurairi ne abu-Usman se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : hamarey yahaan hamarey kuchh mehman aaey, mere walid raat ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas baith kar guftgu kya kartey they, wo chaley gaey aur mujh se farmaya : Abdur-Rehman ! tum apne mahmaanon ki sab khidmat bajaa lana . jab Sham hui to ham ne (unke samney ( khana pesh kya, kaha : to unhon-ne inkar kar diya aur kaha : jab ghar ke Malik ( bachchon ke walid ( aaeingey aur hamarey sath khana khaaengey ( ham us waqt khana khaaengey. ( kaha : maine unko bataya ke wo ( mere walid ( tez mizaaj aadmi hain, agar tum ne khana na khaya to mujhey khadsha hai ke mujhey unki taraf se saza milegi. kaha : lekin wo nahi maaney , jab Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aaey to un (ke mutaalliq poochhney ( se pahley unhon-ne koi (aur ( baat shuru na ki. unhon-ne kaha : mehmanon (ki mezbani) se farigh ho gaey ho? ghar walon ne kaha : Allah ki qasam! abhi ham farigh nahi huey, Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kya maine Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ko kaha nahi tha? (hazrat Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : main aik taraf hat gaya unhon-ne awaz di : Abdur-Rehman ! main khisak gaya. phir unhon-ne kaha : aey ahmaq! main tujhey qism deta hun ke agar to meri awaz sun raha hai to aa jaa. Hazrat Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main aa gaya aur maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! mera koi qasoor nahi hai. ye hain aap ke mehman unse poochh lijiye , main unka khana unke paas laya tha, unhon-ne aap ke aaney tak khaney se inkar kar diya, ( Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha to unhon (Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne ( unse ( kaha : kya baat hai? tum ne hamara pesh kya hawa khana kyon qabool nahi kiya? ( Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! main aaj raat ye khana nahi khaaunga. mahmaanon ne kaha Allah ki qism ! ham bhi us waqt tak khana nahi khaaengey jab tak aap nahi khaatey . Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha is shar jaisa ( shar ( , us raat jaisi (raat ( maine kabhi nahi dekhi , tum logon par afsos ! tumhen kya hai? tum logon ne hamari dawat qabool kyon nahi ki? phir Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ( meri ( pehli baat ( na khaney ki qism ( shaitan ki taraf se ( ubhaarney par) thi. chalo , apna mezbani ka khana laao. Hazrat Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir khana laya gaya, Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bismillah padh kar khana khaya aur mehmaanon ne bhi khaya subah hui to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas gaey aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! un logon ne qism poori kar li aur maine tod di (kaha ( phir Hazrat abu Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pura waqia sunaya , ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) farmaya : nahi, tum unse badh kar qism poori karne waley ho, unse behtar ho, (Hazrat Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : mujh tak kaffara dene ki baat nahi pahunchi (mujhey malum nahi ke mere walid ne kaffara diya ya Kab diya. ("
5367,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : 2 aadmiyon ka khana teen ke liye kifaayat karne wala hota hai aur teen ka khana char ko kafi hota hai."
5368,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim aur Yahya bin Habib ne Rooh bin Ubada se hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne bataya, kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna ke aap farma rahe they : aik aadmi ka khana 2 ke liye kafi ho jata hai. aur 2 ka khana char ke liye kafi ho jata hai. aur char ka khana aath (8) ke liye kafi ho jata hai. aur Ishaq ki riwayat mein hai : (hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine suna ke alfaz zikr nahi kiye."
5369,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ibne-Juraij ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
5370,"abu-Muawiya ne hamein Aamash se khabar di, unhon-ne abu Sufiyan se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik aadmi ka khana 2 aadmiyon ke liye kafi ho jata hai aur 2 ka khana char ke liye kafi ho jata hai."
5371,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik aadmi ka khana 2 aadmiyon ke liye kafi ho jata hai. aur 2 aadmiyon ka khana char ke liye kafi ho jata hai. aur char ka khana aath (8) ke liye kafi ho jata hai."
5372,"Yahya qattaan ne Ubaidullah se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kaafir saat (7) aanton mein khata hai jabke momin aik aant mein khata hai."
5373,"abu-Usama aur ibne-Numair ne Ubaidullah se Mamar ne Ayub se (Ubaidullah aur Ayub) donon ne Naafe se unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
5374,"Waqid bin Muhammad-bin Zaid se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Naafe se suna, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik miskeen ko dekha wo uske samney khana rakhtey rahe rakhtey rahe, kaha : wo shakhs bahut zyada khana khata raha unhon (ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : aainda ye shakhs mere yahan na aaey kyonke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : bila shubah kaafir saat (7) aanton mein khata hai."
5375,"Abdur-Rehman ne Sufiyan se, unhon-ne abu-Zubair se unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : momin aik aant se khata hai jabke kaafir saat (7) aanton mein khata hai."
5376,"ibne-Numair ne hamein hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne abu-Zubair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir se unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki, unhon ( ibne-Numair ( ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr nahi kya."
5377,Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : momin aik aant mein khata hai jabke kaafir saat (7) aanton mein khata hai.
5378,Abdul-Azeez bin-Muhammad ne abul-Ala se unhon-ne apne walid se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se un sab ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki.
5379,"Suhel bin Abu-Saleh ne apne walid se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik mehman aaya wo shakhs kaafir tha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske liye aik bakri ka doodh dohney ka hukm diya us ne doodh pi liya phir dusri bakri ka doodh dohney ka hukm diya us ne usko bhi pi liya, phir aik aur) bakri ka doodh dohney (ka hukm diya us ne usko bhi pi liya, yahan tak ke usne isi tarah saat (7) bakriyon ka doodh pi liya phir us ne subah ki to Islam ley aaya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske liye aik bakri ka doodh dohney ka hukm diya us ne wo doodh pi liya phir dusri bakri ka doodh dohney ka hukm diya, wo uska Sara doodh na pi saka to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : musalman aik aant mein peeta hai jabke kaafir saat (7) aanton mein peeta hai."
5380,"Jarir ne Aamash se unhon-ne abu-Hazim se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi kisi khaney mein aib nahi nikala agar koi cheez aapko pasand aati to aap usko kha letey aur agar na-pasand hoti to usey chhod detey."
5381,Zuhair ne hamein Sulaiman Aamash se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5382,Sufiyan ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5383,"aale-Jaada ke aazad karda ghulam abu-Yahya ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko nahi dekha ke aap ne kabhi kisi khaney mein aib nikala ho. agar aapko koi khana marghoob hota (achchha lagta) to usey kha letey aur achchha na lagta to khamosh rehtey."
5384,abu-Hazim ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
